Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}蒂姆·罗宾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}摩根·弗里曼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肖申克的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩先生{\r}\NMr. Dufresne, describe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请描述一下你妻子遇害当晚你们吵架时的情况{\r}\Nthe confrontation you had with your wife the night she was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我非常痛苦{\r}\NIt was very bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她说被我发现反倒轻松多了 再也不用成天提心吊胆的了{\r}\NShe said she was glad I knew, that she hated all the sneaking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.90,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}美国著名的"离婚城市" 凡欲离婚者 在该市住满三个月即可获准离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她还说她要去里诺市和我离婚{\r}\NAnd she said that she wanted a divorce in Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你当时是如何回答她的? - 我告诉她我不会同意{\r}\N- What was your response? - I told her I would not grant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"我怕你活不到在里诺市见我的那天了!"{\r}\N"I'll see you in hell before I see you in Reno."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}据你邻居的证词 杜弗瑞恩先生 这是你当时的回答{\r}\NThose were your words, according to your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许吧{\r}\NIf they say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我的确不记得了 当时完全气昏头了{\r}\NI really don't remember. I was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们吵完架之后发生了什么事?{\r}\NWhat happened after you argued with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她收拾了一包东西{\r}\NShe packed a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她收了包东西 搬到昆汀先生那儿去住了{\r}\NShe packed a bag to go and stay with Mr. Quentin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}格伦·昆汀 斯诺登俱乐部高尔夫教练{\r}\NGlenn Quentin, golf pro at the Snowden Hills Country Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}其被你发现与你妻子偷情{\r}\Nwhom you had discovered was your wife's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你有没有尾随她?{\r}\NDid you follow her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我先是去的酒吧{\r}\NI went to a few bars first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}之后 我开车去昆汀家找他们 但他们不在{\r}\NLater, I drove to his house to confront them. They weren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我把车停在路岔口{\r}\NI parked in the turnout...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在车里等{\r}\Nand waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当时你有什么企图?{\r}\NWith what intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我自己到现在也说不清{\r}\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当时我心里很乱{\r}\NI was confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}又喝了不少酒{\r}\Ndrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想{\r}\NI think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}顶多也就是想吓吓他们而已{\r}\Nmostly I wanted to scare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们回来后 你就进屋杀了他们{\r}\NWhen they arrived, you went up to the house and murdered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有 我开始清醒过来{\r}\NNo.I was sobering up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}回到车子里 然后开车回家 想着睡一觉会好过一些{\r}\NI got back in the car and I drove home to sleep it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}半路上 我停车把枪扔进了Royal河里{\r}\NAlong the way, I threw my gun into the Royal River.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这一点我记得很清楚{\r}\NI've been very clear on this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}离奇的是次日一早清洁女佣发现{\r}\NI get hazy where the cleaning woman shows up the following morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你妻子和她的情人在床上{\r}\Nand finds your wife in bed with her lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被点三八口径的子弹打得如同马蜂窝一般{\r}\Nriddled with.38-caliber bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不觉得这种巧合来得太蹊跷了吗? 还是只有我这么认为{\r}\NDoes that strike you as a fantastic coincidence, or is it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}的确很蹊跷{\r}\NYes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然而你仍旧坚持在凶案发生前{\r}\NYet you still maintain you threw your gun into the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你已经把枪扔进河里{\r}\Nbefore the murders took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这个说法倒是很省事{\r}\NThat's very convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是事实{\r}\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}警方花三天时间摸遍了整条河道 并没找到一把枪{\r}\NThe police dragged that river for three days, and nary a gun was found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因此也就无法鉴定命中受害者的那些子弹{\r}\Nso no comparison could be made between your gun and the bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是否与你那把枪的弹道相吻合{\r}\Ntaken from the bloodstained corpses of the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这对你来说同样非常省事{\r}\NAnd that also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是吗 杜弗瑞恩先生?{\r}\Nis very convenient. Isn't it, Mr. Dufresne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}恰恰因为我是无辜的 先生{\r}\NSince I am innocent of this crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所以找不到枪反倒对我非常麻烦{\r}\NI find it decidedly inconvenient that the gun was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诸位陪审员 你们听到了所有的证据{\r}\NLadies and gentlemen, you've heard all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被告曾到过凶案现场 并留下脚印{\r}\NWe have the accused at the scene of the crime. We have footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}散落在现场的子弹上有被告的指纹{\r}\NBullets on the ground bearing his fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有一只打碎的酒瓶 同样有他的指纹{\r}\NA broken bourbon bottle, likewise with fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}最重要的是{\r}\NAnd most of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一位漂亮的年轻妇人和她的情人{\r}\Nwe have a beautiful young woman and her lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}双双死在对方的怀抱中{\r}\Nlying dead in each other's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们是有过错{\r}\NThey had sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他们的过错是否严重到{\r}\NBut was their crime so great...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}需要付出生命作为代价呢?{\r}\Nas to merit a death sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在你们作出结论之前{\r}\NWhile you think about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请先看看这个{\r}\Nthink about this:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一只左轮手枪只能填装六颗子弹 而不是八颗{\r}\NA revolver holds six bullets, not eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所以我认定这不是一时冲动才犯下的罪行{\r}\NI submit that this was not a hot-blooded crime of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}即使那不能被宽恕 至少还可以理解{\r}\NThat at least could be understood, if not condoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是!{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是一次复仇行为{\r}\NThis was revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}出于一种特别残忍 冷血的本性{\r}\Nof a much more brutal, cold-blooded nature. Consider this:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}想想看 每个受害人身中四枪{\r}\NFour bullets per victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总共开了八枪 而不是六枪{\r}\NNot six shots fired, but eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那表明他打完一轮子弹后{\r}\NThat means that he fired the gun empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}曾停下来填装子弹{\r}\Nand then stopped to reload...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后继续向受害人开枪{\r}\Nso that he could shoot each of them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每人补射一枪{\r}\NAn extra bullet per lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}正中头部!{\r}\Nright in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩先生 你的冷酷无情 不知悔改让人震惊{\r}\NYou strike me as a particularly icy and remorseless man, Mr. Dufresne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看到你都令我心寒齿冷{\r}\NIt chills my blood just to look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}依据缅因州赋予我的权利{\r}\NBy the power vested in me by the state of Maine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我判处你连服两项终身监禁{\r}\NI hereby order you to serve two life sentences back-to-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}分别告慰两位受害人 退庭!{\r}\None for each of your victims. So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}坐!{\r}\NSit.
