Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}右边 右边{\r}\NRight. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}左边{\r}\NLeft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不用问 入狱的第一夜是最难熬的{\r}\NThe first night's the toughest. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}像刚出生那天一样光着屁股 被他们驱赶前行{\r}\NThey march you in naked as the day you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}除虱粉蜇得你浑身火烧火燎地痛 眼睛几乎半瞎{\r}\Nskin burning and half-blind from that delousing shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当他们把你丢进牢房 砰地关上铁栅栏{\r}\NAnd when they put you in that cell...and those bars slam home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那时你才真的回过神儿来 这是玩儿真的!{\r}\Nthat's when you know it's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}眨眼间过去的生活便离你远去{\r}\NOld life blown away in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么都没留下 却留给你大把的时间去想念过去{\r}\NNothing left but all the time in the world to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}大部分新来的犯人在第一晚都近乎要发疯{\r}\NMost new fish come close to madness the first night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总会有人绷不住 痛哭流涕{\r}\NSomebody always breaks down crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一贯如此{\r}\NHappens every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们关心的问题是{\r}\NThe only question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谁是这第一个哭出来的人?{\r}\Nwho's it going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是一个可以拿来打赌的绝佳问题{\r}\NIt's as good a thing to bet on as any, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我把赌注押在安迪·杜弗瑞恩身上{\r}\NI had my money on Andy Dufresne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}熄灯{\r}\NLights out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我还记得我在这里的第一夜{\r}\NI remember my first night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那似乎已经是很久以前的事了{\r}\NSeems like a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 菜鸟{\r}\NHey, fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}菜鸟 菜鸟 菜鸟 菜鸟～{\r}\NFish, fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你干嘛呢? 怕黑了吗?{\r}\NWhat are you, scared of the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我打赌 你恨不得你老爸从没叉过你老妈{\r}\NBet you wish your daddy never dicked your mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}小猪猪! 小肉肉! 真想要你给我爽一下{\r}\NPiggy! Pork! I want me a pork chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们总是要戏弄刚入狱的人{\r}\NThe boys always go fishing with first-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不逗哭一个不算完{\r}\NAnd they don't quit till they reel someone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 大屁股{\r}\NHey, Fat Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}大屁股!{\r}\NFat Ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}和我说说话吧小子{\r}\NTalk to me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你在哪儿 我都听见你喘气儿了{\r}\NI know you're there. I can hear you breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别听那些傻B瞎掰 你听到没有?{\r}\NDon't you listen to these nitwits, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这地方没那么差{\r}\NThis place ain't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}告诉你为什么{\r}\NTell you what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我可以带你四处走走 让你感觉就像在家一样{\r}\NI'll introduce you around, make you feel right at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我认识一对壮得像牛一样的同志哥{\r}\NI know a couple of big old bull queers that'd just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们一定很乐意跟你混个脸熟{\r}\NIove to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有你那又白又嫩的大屁股{\r}\NEspecially that big, white, mushy butt of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}噢上帝!{\r}\NGod!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不该在这里{\r}\NI don't belong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 嗨 有人胜出了 - 我要回家{\r}\N- We have a winner! - I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}大屁股率先撞线{\r}\NAnd it's Fat Ass by a nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}小菜鸟! 小菜鸟!{\r}\NFresh fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我要回家!{\r}\NI want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我要见我妈妈{\r}\NI want my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我干过你妈妈啦! 她没那么好啦!{\r}\NI had your mother! She wasn't that great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}又他妈在臭屁什么基督的话?{\r}\NWhat the Christ is this horseshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你亵渎神明 我要向典狱长告发{\r}\NHe blasphemed. I'll tell the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等我用警棍叉烂你的屁眼你再去告吧{\r}\NYou'll tell him with my baton up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}放我出去{\r}\NLet me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你他妈个饭桶样 想搞什么飞机?{\r}\NWhat is your malfunction, you fat barrel of monkey spunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}求您了! 我没想过会被关起来{\r}\NPlease! I ain't supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是我干的{\r}\NNot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我可没心情数到三 连一我都不数{\r}\NI won't count to three. Not even to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你马上闭嘴 不然我给你来段摇篮曲!{\r}\NYou shut up, or I'll sing you a lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 别说了 呆子 - 求您了 这件事弄错了{\r}\NShut up, man. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}您不了解 我不知道会被送到这儿来{\r}\NYou don't understand. I'm not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把门打开{\r}\NOpen that cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也是! 这里被他们弄得就像他妈的监狱{\r}\NMe neither! They run this place like a fucking prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你个婊子养的{\r}\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}长官 算了{\r}\NCaptain, take it easy!
