Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我向上帝和耶稣发誓 叫你们吃不了兜着走{\r}\NI swear by God and Jesus, you will all visit the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们这些狗杂种一个都别想溜{\r}\NEvery last motherfucker in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}叫值班的过来 把这坨臭大粪弄到医务室去{\r}\NCall the trustees. Take that tub of shit down to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩的第一晚 让我输了两包烟{\r}\NHis first night in the joint, Dufresne cost me two packs of cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}整个晚上他都一声不响{\r}\NHe never made a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}北仓三楼 到齐{\r}\NTier 3 north, clear count!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}北仓二楼 到齐{\r}\NTier 2 north, clear count.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}南仓三楼 到齐{\r}\NTier 3 south, clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}转向楼梯!{\r}\NPrepare to roll out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}齐步走!{\r}\NRoll out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那东西你吃不吃?{\r}\NAre you going to eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我还没想过{\r}\NI hadn't planned on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}能给我吗?{\r}\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}啊! 白白胖胖的{\r}\NThat's nice and ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杰克说谢谢你{\r}\NJake says thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它从制板车间上面的窝里掉下来{\r}\NFell out of his nest over by the plate shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我得照顾它长大到会飞为止{\r}\NI'm going to look after him until he's big enough to fly.
