Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}都给我拿过来 我来给它们排排队{\r}\NSend them down. I want them lined up...
