Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德 我有点替你脸红啊 你的马儿真不给你长脸{\r}\NThat's a shame about your horse coming in last and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不过我可爱死我那匹马儿了{\r}\NBut I sure do love that winning horse of mine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等见了他一定得结结实实地亲他一口{\r}\NI owe that boy a big kiss when I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你干嘛不分几根烟给他? 走运的龟孙子!{\r}\NWhy don't you give him some of your cigarettes instead? Lucky fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 泰利奥!{\r}\NHey, Tyrell.
