Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哈德利把他的脑袋打开了花{\r}\NHadley busted his head up pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}晚上医生都回家了{\r}\NDoc had gone home for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可怜的家伙就那么躺到天亮{\r}\NPoor bastard lay there till this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到那会儿怎么救都晚了{\r}\NBy then, there wasn't nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他叫什么名字?{\r}\NWhat was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你说什么?{\r}\NWhat'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只是想问有人知道他的名字吗?{\r}\NI was just wondering if anyone knew his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}关他妈你什么屁事 新来的?{\r}\NWhat the fuck do you care, new fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别他妈打听他的名字了 他死了{\r}\NDoesn't fucking matter what his name was. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.35,0:23:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 有人找过你吗?{\r}\NAnybody come at you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有人搞过你吗?{\r}\NAnybody get to you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嗨 在这里我们都需要朋友{\r}\NHey, we all need friends in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我可以做你的朋友{\r}\NI could be a friend to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.70,0:24:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不好上手啊{\r}\NHard to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我喜欢{\r}\NI like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}最初那段时间的安迪一直沉默寡言{\r}\NAndy kept pretty much to himself at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许他心里有很多想法{\r}\NI guess he had a lot on his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在努力适应大牢里的生活{\r}\Ntrying to adapt to life on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.19,0:24:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他是一个月之后才开口{\r}\NWasn't until a month went by before he opened his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.59,0:24:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}和一个人一次说话超过两句以上的{\r}\Nto say more than two words to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.16,0:24:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}实不相瞒{\r}\NAs it turned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.20,0:24:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那个人就是我{\r}\Nthat somebody was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.84,0:24:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是安迪·杜弗瑞恩{\r}\NI'm Andy Dufresne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杀妻银行家{\r}\NWife-killing banker.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.82,0:25:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你为什么杀她?{\r}\NWhy'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.59,0:25:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是我杀的 既然你有此一问{\r}\NI didn't, since you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你算来对地方了{\r}\NYou're going to fit right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.32,0:25:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这儿的每个人都是无辜的 你还不知道吧?{\r}\NEverybody in here's innocent. Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.63,0:25:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}海伍德 你怎么进来的? 什么都没做 我被律师设计了{\r}\N- What you in here for? - Didn't do it. Lawyer fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}传说你很拽啊{\r}\NRumor has it you're a real cold fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你觉得自己尿得比别人高一点儿 是吗?{\r}\NYou think your shit smells sweeter than most. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.44,0:25:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你看呢?{\r}\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.27,0:25:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说实话 我还不知道{\r}\NTo tell you the truth, I haven't made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你有办法弄东西进来{\r}\NI understand you're a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这事儿大家一向都知道{\r}\NI'm known to locate certain things from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不知道你能不能帮我弄个鹤嘴槌进来? 什么?{\r}\NI wonder if you might get me a rock hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.02,0:25:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}鹤嘴槌!{\r}\NA rock hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 那是什么东西? 你要来干嘛? - 你担心什么?{\r}\N- What is it and why? - What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.73,0:25:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那要是把牙刷我也懒得问你 直接给你开价{\r}\NFor a toothbrush, I wouldn't ask. I'd quote a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.63,0:25:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}因为牙刷伤不了人 听懂没有?{\r}\NBut a toothbrush is a non-lethal object, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.64,0:25:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我明白了{\r}\NFair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.47,0:26:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}鹤嘴槌大概长六到七英寸的样子{\r}\NA rock hammer is about six or seven inches long.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 看起来像个小号的镐头 - 镐头?{\r}\N- Looks like a miniature pickax. - Pickax?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.84,0:26:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 敲石头用的 - 石头?{\r}\NFor rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.65,0:26:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}石英石吗?{\r}\NQuartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.94,0:26:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}石英{\r}\NQuartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.82,0:26:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有云母 页岩{\r}\NAnd some mica, shale...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.52,0:26:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}石灰石{\r}\Nlimestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.02,0:26:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就这些?{\r}\NSo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.09,0:26:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的 我喜欢玩儿石头{\r}\NSo I'm a rock hound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}曾经玩儿过一段时间 现在想重新捡起来{\r}\NAt least I was in my old life. I'd like to be again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.73,0:26:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你别是想用你的玩具敲谁的脑袋吧{\r}\NOr maybe you'd like to sink your toy into somebody's skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不会 我在这里没有仇人{\r}\NNo, I have no enemies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.11,0:26:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有? 你先等等{\r}\NNo? Wait a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.04,0:26:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}话都传开了{\r}\NWord gets around.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.31,0:26:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}姐妹们特喜欢你{\r}\NThe Sisters have taken quite a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}尤其是伯格斯{\r}\NEspecially Bogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.98,0:26:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}跟他们说我不是同性恋也没用吗?{\r}\NDon't suppose it would help if I told them I'm not homosexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.62,0:26:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们也不是{\r}\NNeither are they.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.26,0:26:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}同性恋怎么说也是人 这几个是畜牲{\r}\NYou have to be human first. They don't qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.23,0:27:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}霸王可以硬上弓 他们就知道这个{\r}\NBull queers take by force. That's all they want or understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.84,0:27:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我要是你 得在后脑勺再安双眼睛{\r}\NIf I were you, I'd grow eyes in the back of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 谢谢你的提醒 - 不客气 这个不收费{\r}\N- Thanks for the advice. - Well, that's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.68,0:27:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你知道我的顾虑了吧?{\r}\NYou understand my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.84,0:27:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要是我有麻烦也不用鹤嘴槌 行了吧?{\r}\NIf there's trouble, I won't use the rock hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.35,0:27:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么你八成是想越狱 在墙根挖条地道什么的?{\r}\NThen I'd guess you want to escape. Tunnel under the wall, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.29,0:27:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我说错了么? 你笑什么?{\r}\NWhat did I miss? What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.39,0:27:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等看见鹤嘴槌你就明白了{\r}\NYou'll understand when you see the rock hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.93,0:27:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}买这个东西一般要多少钱?{\r}\NWhat's an item like this usually go for?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.36,0:27:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}七美元 随便一家石器店都买得到{\r}\NSeven dollars in any rock-and-gem shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我一般抽两成{\r}\NMy normal markup's 20 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.03,0:27:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但这东西情况特别{\r}\NBut this is a specialty item.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.60,0:27:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}风险增加 价钱也得增加 一口价 10元{\r}\NRisk goes up, price goes up. Let's make it an even 10 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.28,0:27:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那就10元吧{\r}\NTen it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.35,0:27:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}依我看你那是白花钱{\r}\NWaste of money, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.65,0:27:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么?{\r}\NWhy's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这儿的条子喜欢搞突击检查{\r}\NFolks around this joint love surprise inspections.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.99,0:27:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被他们发现 你这东西就保不住了{\r}\NThey find it, you're going to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:27:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要是真被他们发现 你可别把我卖了{\r}\NIf they catch you, you don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.46,0:28:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你要是把我扯出来 今后就不用来找我拿东西了{\r}\NMention my name, we never do business again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哪怕一副鞋带一根口香糖都别想 记住没有?{\r}\NNot for shoelaces or a stick of gum. Now you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.13,0:28:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}放心好了{\r}\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.90,0:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 你叫...{\r}\NThank you, Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.20,0:28:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德{\r}\NRed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.97,0:28:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}叫我瑞德就行{\r}\NName's Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.71,0:28:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这名字怎么来的?{\r}\NWhy do they call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可能因为我是爱尔兰人吧{\r}\NMaybe it's because I'm Irish.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.29,0:28:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我现在明白为什么有人说他是个异类了{\r}\NI could see why some of the boys took him for snobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他有股子气定神闲的劲儿{\r}\NHe had a quiet way about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一言一行都跟周围人不一样{\r}\Na walk and a talk that just wasn't normal around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.30,0:28:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他信步走去{\r}\NHe strolled...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.97,0:28:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像是一名在公园里散步的男子 了无羁绊{\r}\Nlike a man in the park without a care or a worry in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.37,0:28:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}仿佛穿了件无形的外套 把他和这个地方隔绝开来{\r}\NLike he had on an invisible coat that would shield him from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:28:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说句良心话{\r}\NI think it'd be fair to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.48,0:29:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}第一次接触我就对安迪产生了好感{\r}\NI liked Andy from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.25,0:29:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点! 有人得抓点紧了{\r}\NLet's go! Some of us got a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.39,0:29:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}动起来 快点 动起来{\r}\NMove it! Come on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.50,0:29:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}最近还好吧? 你老婆对你怎么样?{\r}\NHow you doing? How's the wife treating you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.56,0:29:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德!{\r}\NRed!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.57,0:29:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪说中了{\r}\NAndy was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.28,0:29:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我最终明白他为什么发笑了{\r}\NI finally got the joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.81,0:30:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}估计要花六百年{\r}\NIt would take a man about 600 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.41,0:30:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}才能用这东西在墙根挖出一条地道{\r}\Nto tunnel under the wall with one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.65,0:30:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 要书吗? - 今天不要{\r}\N- Book? - Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.13,0:30:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要书吗?{\r}\NBook?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.47,0:30:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}交给杜弗瑞恩{\r}\NDelivery for Dufresne.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.32,0:30:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩 这是你的书{\r}\NHere's your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.93,0:30:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.07,0:31:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩 漂白粉快用完了 你去后面拿点来{\r}\NWe're running low on hexite. Get on back and fetch us up some.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.45,0:31:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这东西会弄瞎你的眼睛{\r}\NThis will blind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.38,0:31:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}亲爱的 别紧张{\r}\NHoney, hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.33,0:31:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就对了 你越反抗{\r}\NThat's it. You fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.50,0:32:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我感觉越刺激{\r}\NBetter that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.21,0:32:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我很想告诉你 安迪打得很漂亮{\r}\NI wish I could tell you Andy fought the good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.51,0:32:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}姐妹们没能把他怎么样{\r}\Nand the Sisters let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.08,0:32:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望我可以这么告诉你{\r}\NI wish I could tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.12,0:32:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是监狱不是童话世界{\r}\Nbut prison is no fairy-tale world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.22,0:32:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他从没说过是谁干的{\r}\NHe never said who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.42,0:32:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我们都明白是怎么回事{\r}\NBut we all knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.86,0:32:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}日子就这样一天天过去{\r}\NThings went on like that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.76,0:32:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}监狱生活就像例行公事{\r}\NPrison life consists of routine...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.53,0:32:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}除此之外还是例行公事{\r}\Nand then more routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.01,0:32:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪脸上不断出现新的伤痕{\r}\NEvery so often, Andy would show up with fresh bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.01,0:32:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}姐妹们不断侵犯他{\r}\NThe Sisters kept at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.08,0:32:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时他能逃脱{\r}\NSometimes he was able to fight them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.35,0:32:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时不能{\r}\NSometimes not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.02,0:32:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是安迪的监狱生活{\r}\NAnd that's how it went for Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是他的例行公事{\r}\NThat was his routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.36,0:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我相信最初那两年是他最糟糕的两年{\r}\NI do believe those first two years were the worst for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也相信如果日子继续这样过下去的话{\r}\NAnd I also believe that if things had gone on that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.00,0:33:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这个地方早晚会把他给毁了{\r}\Nthis place would have got the best of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.20,0:33:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是 在1949年的春天{\r}\NBut then, in the spring of 1949...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}监狱管理层决定{\r}\Nthe powers that be decided:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.31,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}制板车间的屋顶需要修整{\r}\NThe roof of the license-plate factory needs resurfacing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.84,0:33:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我需要12名志愿者工作一周{\r}\NI need a dozen volunteers for a week's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们都知道{\r}\NAs you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.95,0:33:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}特殊的任务意味着特殊的待遇{\r}\Nspecial detail carries with it special privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是一次户外劳务{\r}\NIt was outdoor detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而五月份是户外劳务的最他妈好的时间了{\r}\Nand May is one damned fine month to be working outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.03,0:33:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}排好队{\r}\NStay in line there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有一百多人报名参加志愿劳务{\r}\NMore than a hundred men volunteered for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}威勒斯·E·安戈{\r}\NWallace E. Unger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.50,0:33:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}艾力斯·瑞丁（瑞德的大名）{\r}\NEllis Redding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.07,0:33:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你看出来了吧?{\r}\NWouldn't you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.08,0:33:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我和我的朋友们都被选中了{\r}\NMe and some fellows I know were among the names called.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.58,0:33:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪·杜弗瑞恩{\r}\NAndrew Dufresne.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.98,0:33:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这只花了我们每人一包烟的代价{\r}\NIt only cost us a pack of smokes per man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.42,0:34:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我当然还是照例抽两成{\r}\NI made my usual 20 percent, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.09,0:34:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那牛B律师从德州打长途给我{\r}\NSo this big-shot lawyer calls me long-distance from Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.76,0:34:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我说 "什么事? "{\r}\NI say, "Yeah?"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.59,0:34:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他说 "很抱歉通知你 你哥哥刚刚过世"{\r}\NHe says, " Sorry to inform you, but your brother just died."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.43,0:34:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这真让人难过{\r}\N- I'm sorry to hear that. - I'm not. He was an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.19,0:34:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我可不难过 那混蛋死就死了 跑那么多年 早当他死了{\r}\NRan off years ago. Figured him for dead.
