Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.21,0:38:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}象棋 才是王者的游戏{\r}\N- Chess. Now there's a game of kings. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.05,0:39:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}文明 战略 什么?{\r}\NCivilized. Strategic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.45,0:39:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有一大套见鬼的规则 我讨厌规则{\r}\NAnd a total fucking mystery. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}改天我教教你吧{\r}\NLet me teach you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.06,0:39:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好的{\r}\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.49,0:39:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们可以一起弄个棋盘{\r}\NWe could get a board together.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.46,0:39:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你找对人了 我什么都能弄来 你知道噻?{\r}\NYou're talking to the right man. I can get things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.73,0:39:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}棋盘我们可以花钱买 棋子我想自己刻{\r}\NWe might do business on a board, and I'll carve the pieces myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.94,0:39:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}白棋用雪花石膏 黑棋用皂石 你看怎么样?{\r}\NOne side in alabaster, one in soapstone. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.84,0:39:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我看那得花好几年{\r}\NI think it'll take years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.44,0:39:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}时间不是问题 问题是没有石头{\r}\NYears I got. What I don't have are the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.18,0:39:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这院子里能捡到的都太小了{\r}\NPickings are pretty slim in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.35,0:39:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而且大多是鹅卵石{\r}\NPebbles, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.52,0:39:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪 我们得算是朋友了吧?{\r}\NWe're getting to be kind of friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.19,0:39:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想是的{\r}\NYeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.39,0:39:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我能问你个问题吗?{\r}\NCan I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.40,0:39:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你为什么做出那种事?{\r}\NWhy'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.07,0:39:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是被冤枉的 瑞德{\r}\NI'm innocent, Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.83,0:39:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}跟这儿其他人一样{\r}\NJust like everybody else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.21,0:39:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你是怎么进来的?{\r}\NWhat are you in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.48,0:40:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}和你一样 谋杀{\r}\NMurder. Same as you.
