Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.72,0:40:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肖申克唯一有罪的人{\r}\NOnly guilty man in Shawshank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.45,0:41:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她在哪儿唱歌呢?{\r}\NWhere's the canary?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你怎么知道的?{\r}\NHow did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.65,0:41:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道什么了?{\r}\N- How did I know what? - So you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.13,0:41:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这么说你不知道? 跟我来!{\r}\NCome.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.82,0:41:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她就在里面{\r}\NThis is where the canary is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.59,0:41:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听到我家里有女人唱歌很惊讶是吗?{\r}\NQuite a surprise to hear a woman singing in my house, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.43,0:41:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}的确非常令我...{\r}\NThat's quite a...
