Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德{\r}\NRed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.74,0:41:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等一下 先别说话{\r}\NWait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.68,0:41:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她出场了{\r}\NHere she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.45,0:41:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我太喜欢看她摆弄头发那副骚样儿了{\r}\NI like this part when she does that shit with her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.51,0:41:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道 这个月已经看了三遍了{\r}\NI know. I've seen it three times this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.45,0:41:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}吉尔达 你打扮好了吗?{\r}\NGilda, are you decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我?{\r}\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.19,0:41:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}天呐 爱死啦{\r}\NGod, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.13,0:42:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你有办法弄东西进来{\r}\NI understand you're a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.14,0:42:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这事儿大家一向都知道 你想要什么?{\r}\NI'm known to locate certain things from time to time. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 丽塔·海华斯 - 什么?{\r}\N- Rita Hayworth. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.78,0:42:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你能搞到她吗?{\r}\NCan you get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.54,0:42:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这么说你就是强尼了 久闻大名{\r}\NSo this is Johnny Farrel. I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.15,0:42:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你得等几个星期 - 那么久?{\r}\N- Take a few weeks. - Weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.65,0:42:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我这分钟又没把她藏在裤裆里 抱歉我这么粗鲁{\r}\NI don't have her stuffed down the front of my pants right now, sorry to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.62,0:42:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我能拿到{\r}\NBut I'll get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.16,0:42:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}放心好了!{\r}\NRelax.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.36,0:42:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢!{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.25,0:42:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 出去遛遛腿! - 可是我得换带子!{\r}\N- Get out! - I got to change reels!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.25,0:42:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我叫你他妈的滚出去!{\r}\NI said fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.39,0:43:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不打算尖叫吗?{\r}\NAin't you going to scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.10,0:43:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们做个了断吧!{\r}\NLet's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.07,0:43:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}操 我鼻梁断了!{\r}\NHe broke my fucking nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.38,0:43:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在{\r}\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.08,0:43:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我要拉开拉链{\r}\NI'm going to open my fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.52,0:43:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我给你吞什么你就吞什么{\r}\Nand you'll swallow what I give you to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.42,0:43:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后是罗斯 你把他鼻子打坏了{\r}\NThen you'll swallow Rooster's. You broke his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.23,0:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他得找点补偿回来{\r}\NHe ought to have something to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.56,0:43:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的命根子到我嘴里就会跟你分家{\r}\NYou put it in my mouth, you lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.63,0:43:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 你还没明白{\r}\NNo, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.57,0:43:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你敢那样 我就把这八英寸全部插到你耳朵里{\r}\NDo that and I'll put all eight inches of this in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.80,0:43:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}行啊 但你得知道大脑受到重创时{\r}\NAll right, but you should know that sudden, serious brain injury...
