Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.61,0:43:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}实话告诉你 这种咬劲儿之大{\r}\NIn fact, I hear the bite reflex is so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.91,0:43:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}得用铁棍才能把他的嘴巴撬开{\r}\Nthey have to pry the victim's jaws open...with a crowbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.92,0:44:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你他妈从哪儿知道的?{\r}\NWhere do you get this shit?
