Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.64,0:44:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不识字? 你这无知的杂种!{\r}\Nilliterate? You ignorant fuck!
