Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.24,0:44:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}伯格斯没把任何东西放进安迪的嘴里{\r}\NBogs didn't put anything in Andy's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.41,0:44:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他的同伙也没有{\r}\NAnd neither did his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.91,0:44:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们只是把他打了个半死{\r}\NWhat they did do is beat him within an inch of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.41,0:44:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪在医务所躺了一个月{\r}\NAndy spent a month in the infirmary.
