Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.81,0:52:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 有问题吗? - 你作图书管理员有多久了?{\r}\N - Any questions? - How long have you been librarian?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.82,0:53:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我1905年入狱 1912年他们安排我作图书管理员{\r}\NI come here in '05, and they made me librarian in 1912.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.16,0:53:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你以前有助手吗?{\r}\NAnd have you ever had an assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.60,0:53:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有 没什么要帮忙的 真的{\r}\NNo. Not much to it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.77,0:53:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么现在? 为什么是我?{\r}\NWhy me? Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.43,0:53:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这我可不知道{\r}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.94,0:53:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但有人来这儿和我作个伴我倒非常欢迎 杜弗瑞恩!{\r}\NBut it'd be nice to have some company down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.22,0:53:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就是他 你要找的人{\r}\NThat's him. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.16,0:53:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我叫迪金斯{\r}\NI'm Dekins.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.73,0:53:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我一直想...{\r}\NI was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.03,0:53:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}替我孩子的学业办一份信托基金{\r}\Nabout setting up some kind of trust fund for my kids' educations.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.81,0:53:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我明白了{\r}\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.71,0:53:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧...{\r}\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.38,0:53:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让我们坐下来慢慢谈好吗?{\r}\NWhy don't we have a seat and talk it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.22,0:54:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯 你能找张纸还有铅笔吗?{\r}\NDo you have a piece of paper and a pencil?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.87,0:54:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.83,0:54:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么...{\r}\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.67,0:54:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}迪金斯先生{\r}\NMister Dekins...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.24,0:54:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}接着安迪说 "迪金斯先生...{\r}\NAnd then Andy says, "Mr. Dekins...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.54,0:54:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你想让你的儿子去哈佛还是耶鲁?"{\r}\Ndo you want your sons to go to Harvard or Yale?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.74,0:54:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他不可能那么说!{\r}\NHe didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.15,0:54:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}上帝可以作证{\r}\NAs God as my witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.92,0:54:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}迪金斯愣了一下{\r}\NDekins blinked for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.85,0:54:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}然后傻笑起来 他甚至还握了安迪的手{\r}\Nthen he laughed and actually shook Andy's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.42,0:54:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}扯淡吧!{\r}\NMy ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.82,0:54:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}握他的手啊! 我跟你们讲 我高兴得差点尿裤子{\r}\NShook his hand, I tell you, I near soiled myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.03,0:54:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只要穿上西服打起领带 桌子上再来个扭着草裙舞的姑娘{\r}\NAll he needed was a suit and tie and a jiggly hula gal on his desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.50,0:54:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪就是"杜弗瑞恩先生"了 各位!{\r}\Nhe'd have been "Mr. Dufresne " if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.30,0:54:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪 交上新朋友了?{\r}\NMaking a few friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.62,0:54:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只是一个可以提供可靠理财计划的犯人{\r}\NI'm a convicted murderer who provides sound financial planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.14,0:55:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也就是个不错的宠物罢了{\r}\NIt's a wonderful pet to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.68,0:55:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}至少你不用在洗衣房熬着了 对吧?{\r}\NGot you out of the laundry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.01,0:55:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许还能多做点事情{\r}\NIt might do more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.15,0:55:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}扩大图书馆怎么样 弄些新书进来{\r}\NHow about expanding the library. Get some new books.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.05,0:55:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你有那能耐倒不如弄张台球桌进来{\r}\NIf you ask for something, ask for a pool table.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.36,0:55:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你打算怎么办? 我是说...{\r}\NHow do you expect to do that? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.56,0:55:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}怎么弄来新书 "杜弗瑞恩先生" 不介意的话{\r}\Nget new books in here, "Mr. Dufresne, if you please."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.00,0:55:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我找典狱长要经费{\r}\NI'll ask the warden for funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.93,0:55:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}噢 孩子 孩子 我在这儿经历了六个典狱长{\r}\NSix wardens have been through here in my tenure, and I've learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.44,0:55:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我学到一条亘古不变的普世真理{\r}\None immutable, universal truth:
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.97,0:55:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当你要钱的时候 没有一个典狱长{\r}\NNot one born whose asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.58,0:55:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不把他们的屁眼绷的跟小军鼓一样紧的{\r}\Nwouldn't pucker up tighter than a snare drum when you ask for funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.38,0:55:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 预算不够用 - 这我了解{\r}\N- The budget's stretched thin as it is. - I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.48,0:55:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或许我可以写信向州参议员申请经费{\r}\NMaybe I could write the state senate and request funds from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.12,0:55:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们只会花纳税人的钱为监狱做三件事{\r}\NThey have only three ways to spend the taxpayers' money for prisons:
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.43,0:55:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}加高围墙 修建牢房 增派守卫!{\r}\NMore walls, more bars, more guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.06,0:55:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果您准许 我想试试看 每周写一封信{\r}\NI'd like to try, with permission. A letter a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.93,0:55:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 他们不能永远不当回事儿 - 他们当然能!{\r}\N- They can't ignore me forever. - Sure can.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.93,0:55:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但你要是写着高兴那就写吧{\r}\NBut you write your letters if it makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我替你寄出去 怎么样?{\r}\NI'll even mail them for you. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.17,0:56:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}于是 安迪开始每周写一封信{\r}\NSo Andy started writing a letter a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.18,0:56:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像他说的那样{\r}\Njust like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.95,0:56:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺顿说的也没错{\r}\NAnd like Norton said...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.79,0:56:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪没得到过任何答复{\r}\NAndy got no answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.46,0:56:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到次年四月时 安迪已经在帮肖申克的一半狱警报税了{\r}\NThe following April, he did tax returns for half the guards at Shawshank.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.70,0:56:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}又过了一年 所有狱警都来找他帮忙{\r}\NYear after that, he did them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.20,0:56:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}包括典狱长的都由他处理了{\r}\Nincluding the warden's.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.87,0:56:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}再过一年 他们甚至把狱警联赛的赛程安排在当年的报税期{\r}\NYear after that, they rescheduled the intramural season...to coincide with tax season.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.55,0:56:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}其它监狱球队的狱警们都带着报税单来打比赛{\r}\NThe guards on the opposing teams all remembered to bring their W-2s.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.22,0:56:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就是说莫尔斯比监狱...{\r}\NSo Moresby Prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.76,0:56:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}配给你一支枪 但要你自己付钱{\r}\Nissued you a gun, but you paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.26,0:56:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对 手枪皮套也是{\r}\NRight. The holster too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.16,0:56:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是免税的 你可以把这一项划掉{\r}\NThat's tax-deductible. You can write that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.83,0:57:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没错! 安迪完全像一个正规的会计师{\r}\NYes, sir! Andy was a regular cottage industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.57,0:57:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}由于安迪一个人在报税期忙不过来 有必要配个帮手{\r}\NIn fact, it got so busy at tax time, he was allowed a staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.34,0:57:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德 你可以拿一叠1040号表格给我吗?{\r}\NCould you hand me a stack of 1040s?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.01,0:57:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每年能有一个月的时间离开木工车间 对我来说也相当不错{\r}\NGot me out of the wood shop a month out of the year, and that was fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.08,0:57:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}几年间 寄信那事儿他也从没耽误过{\r}\NAnd still, he kept sending those letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.81,0:57:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德 安迪 布鲁克斯出事了{\r}\NIt's Brooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.19,0:57:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看着门!{\r}\NWatch the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.93,0:57:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 求你了布鲁克斯 别他妈这么冲动! - 别过来!不要过来!{\r}\NPlease, Brooks. - Calm the fuck down. - Stay back! - Stay back, goddamn it! - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.74,0:57:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 怎么闹成这样? - 才还好好的 不知怎么的就冒把刀出来{\r}\NOne second he's fine, then out come the knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.37,0:57:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯 有话好好说 行吗?{\r}\NWe can talk about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.44,0:57:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没啥好说的 我他妈就是要给他一刀{\r}\NThere's nothing to talk about. I'll cut his fucking throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.44,0:57:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}先等等 他把你怎么了?{\r}\NWhat's he done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.38,0:57:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是他们逼我的!{\r}\NIt's what they done!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.55,0:57:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没别的办法{\r}\NI got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.28,0:57:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯你不会伤到海伍德的 大家都知道{\r}\NYou won't hurt Heywood. We all know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.78,0:57:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 对吧 海伍德 你知道吧? - 是 没错 我知道{\r}\N- Right, Heywood? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.49,0:57:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你知道他为什么不会伤到你 因为他是你的朋友 布鲁克斯是个讲理的人{\r}\NHe's a friend of yours, and Brooks is a reasonable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.09,0:58:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 对啊, 你说呢? - 是的!{\r}\NRight, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.13,0:58:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你把刀放下 布鲁克斯{\r}\NSo put the knife down. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.07,0:58:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看着我布鲁克斯 把刀放下{\r}\NPut the knife down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.04,0:58:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯? 你看看他的脖子 看在上帝份儿上{\r}\NLook at his neck, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.90,0:58:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯你看他的脖子 他流血了{\r}\NLook at his neck. He's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.14,0:58:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是唯一可以...{\r}\NIt's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.81,0:58:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}留在这儿的办法{\r}\Nthey'd let me stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.14,0:58:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你这是糊涂了 你肯定不想这样{\r}\NThis is crazy. You don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.75,0:58:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}松手 放下刀{\r}\NPut it, put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.59,0:58:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别紧张{\r}\NTake it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.76,0:58:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不会有事的{\r}\NYou'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.29,0:58:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他没事? 那我呢?{\r}\NHim? What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.16,0:58:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他妈的这个老疯子差点割断我的喉咙{\r}\NCrazy old fool damn near cut my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.77,0:58:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你刮胡子弄烂的口子也不止这么大{\r}\NYou've had worse from shaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.87,0:58:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你到底怎么把他惹毛的?{\r}\NWhat did you do to set him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.17,0:58:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没惹啊 我过来和他道个别而已{\r}\NNothing. I come in here to say farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.01,0:58:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不知道啊? 他的假释批下来了{\r}\NAin't you heard? His parole's come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.01,0:58:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我真搞不懂这是怎么回事{\r}\NI just don't understand what happened in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.01,0:58:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}老家伙发疯了 就像一只痰盂里的老鼠{\r}\NOld man's crazy as a rat in a tin shithouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.02,0:59:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}海伍德你别没完没了{\r}\NThat's enough out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.12,0:59:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我听说把你吓尿裤子了 - 去你的{\r}\N- Heard he had you shitting your pants. - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.12,0:59:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不说话会死啊!{\r}\NWould you knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.29,0:59:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯没发神经{\r}\NBrooks ain't no bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.30,0:59:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他只不过是...他只不过是被体制化了罢了{\r}\NHe's just institutionalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.70,0:59:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}体制化个鸡毛{\r}\N"Institutionalized " my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.83,0:59:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}老头儿在这儿呆了五十年了 海伍德 五十年!{\r}\NThe man's been in here 50 years, Heywood, 50 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.04,0:59:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他就认识这个地方{\r}\NThis is all he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.97,0:59:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在这儿 他是个有地位的人{\r}\NIn here, he's an important man...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.48,0:59:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个有教养的人{\r}\Nan educated man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.38,0:59:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到了外面 他什么都不是{\r}\NOutside, he's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.18,0:59:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只是个双手患有关节炎的假释犯{\r}\NJust a used-up con with arthritis in both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.89,0:59:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可能连一张图书馆的借书证都申请不到{\r}\NProbably couldn't get a library card if he tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.16,0:59:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你听懂我说的话没有?{\r}\NYou know what I'm trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.16,0:59:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德 我听懂了 你说的全是屁话{\r}\NI do believe you're talking out of your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.33,0:59:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}信不信随你大小便{\r}\NYou believe whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.16,0:59:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我得告诉你 这些围墙很吊诡{\r}\NBut I tell you these walls are funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.17,0:59:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}刚来的时候 你会恨它{\r}\NFirst you hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.67,0:59:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}慢慢你就会习惯它{\r}\NThen you get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.51,1:00:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}日子久了...{\r}\NEnough time passes...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.18,1:00:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你会发现你离不开它{\r}\Nyou get so you depend on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.18,1:00:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那就是被体制化了{\r}\NThat's "institutionalized."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.58,1:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}操! 我永远不可能爱上这堵破墙{\r}\NShit. I could never get like that. - Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.82,1:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是吗? 这话等你在这儿呆够布鲁克斯那么久再说{\r}\NWait till you've been here as long as Brooks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.46,1:00:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}太他妈对了{\r}\NGoddamn right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.60,1:00:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们把你送进来渡过余生{\r}\NThey send you here for life...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.20,1:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那也正是他们想要剥夺的{\r}\Nthat's exactly what they take.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.27,1:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总之 去日无多{\r}\NPart that counts, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.88,1:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不能再照顾你了 杰克{\r}\NI can't take care of you no more, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.98,1:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你现在走吧{\r}\NYou go on now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.89,1:00:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你自由了{\r}\NYou're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.65,1:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你自由了{\r}\NYou're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.24,1:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯 祝你好运{\r}\NGood luck, Brooksie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.88,1:01:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}亲爱的伙计们{\r}\NDear fellas:
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.65,1:01:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没法相信外面的东西怎么会跑那么快{\r}\NI can't believe how fast things move on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.16,1:01:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}老头 找死啊?{\r}\NWatch it, old-timer! Want to get killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.06,1:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我小时候就见过一次汽车{\r}\NI saw an automobile once when I was a kid...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.20,1:02:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但现在这东西无处不在{\r}\Nbut now they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.30,1:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}全世界都他妈忙得不可开交{\r}\NThe world went and got itself in a big damn hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.42,1:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}假释委员会安排我住在一家小旅馆 叫 Brewster{\r}\NThe parole board got me into this halfway house...called "The Brewster"...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.36,1:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有一份差事 在Food-Way超市替顾客打包{\r}\Nand a job...bagging groceries at the Food-Way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.23,1:02:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}活儿很忙 我很努力{\r}\NIt's hard work and I try to keep up...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.87,1:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我这双手总是酸痛不已{\r}\Nbut my hands hurt most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.54,1:02:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让你的人给我多套一个袋子{\r}\NMake sure your man double-bags.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.71,1:02:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}上回给我的单层袋子底儿差点烂完了{\r}\NLast time, the bottom near came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.41,1:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}按那位女士说的多套一个袋子 懂了吗?{\r}\NMake sure you double-bag like the lady says. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.55,1:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的 先生 我会的{\r}\NYes, sir. Surely will.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.12,1:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看得出那经理对我不太感冒{\r}\NI don't think the store manager likes me very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.66,1:03:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时下了班以后 我会去公园里喂喂鸽子{\r}\NSometimes after work, I go to the park and feed the birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.39,1:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我一直在念叨{\r}\NI keep thinking...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.13,1:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杰克说不定会飞来和我打个招呼{\r}\NJake might just show up and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.07,1:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但它从没来过{\r}\NBut he never does.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.27,1:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望 不管在哪 它都能过的好 交到新朋友{\r}\NI hope, wherever he is, he's doing okay and making new friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.75,1:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}夜里我总是睡不好{\r}\NI have trouble sleeping at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.78,1:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}老是做恶梦 身体像一直往下掉{\r}\NI have bad dreams like I'm falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.32,1:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}醒来时万分恐惧{\r}\NI wake up scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.75,1:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}经常要想一会儿才知道自己在哪儿{\r}\NSometimes it takes me a while to remember where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.49,1:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许我该搞把枪把 Food- Way抢了 好让他们送我回家{\r}\NMaybe I should get a gun and rob the Food-Way so they'd send me home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.70,1:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}顺便给那个经理来一枪 就当是锦上添花{\r}\NI could shoot the manager while I was at it. Sort of like a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.70,1:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可是我已经太老了 再也干不了这种蠢事了{\r}\NI guess I'm too old for that sort of nonsense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.94,1:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不喜欢这地方{\r}\NI don't like it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.88,1:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我觉得很疲惫 不想继续这样成天提心吊胆的 我决定...{\r}\NI'm tired of being afraid all the time. I've decided...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.72,1:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不这么耗着了{\r}\Nnot to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.29,1:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想他们是不会大惊小怪的{\r}\NI doubt they'll kick up any fuss...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.06,1:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为我这种老不死的犯不上{\r}\Nnot for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.50,1:05:08.19,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯在这儿住过
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.03,1:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我猜他们是不会大惊小怪的 为我这种老不死的犯不上{\r}\N"I doubt they'll kick up any fuss, not for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.34,1:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}另外 还得向海伍德道个歉 请原谅我上次用刀顶着你脖子{\r}\NP.S. Tell Heywood I'm sorry I put a knife to his throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.37,1:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这样我也就安心了 布鲁克斯{\r}\NNo hard feelings. Brooks."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.19,1:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他应该死在这儿的{\r}\NHe should have died in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.69,1:05:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你他妈搞什么东东?{\r}\NWhat the fuck have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.29,1:05:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}简直他妈乱成一锅粥了{\r}\NIt's a goddamn mess, I'll tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.50,1:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这些都是什么? - 我怎么知道 全他妈是寄给你的{\r}\N- What's all this? - You tell me. They're addressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.51,1:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看看吧{\r}\NTake it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.38,1:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"亲爱的杜弗瑞恩先生{\r}\N"Dear Mr. Dufresne:
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.02,1:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}应阁下来函所请事由 州政府特拨付{\r}\NIn response to your inquiries...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.19,1:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}贵图书馆项目经费一笔...{\r}\Nthe state has allocated the enclosed funds for your library project."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.23,1:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}200美元...{\r}\NThis is $ 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.26,1:06:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}此外 州立图书馆亦慷慨捐助{\r}\N"In addition, the library district has generously responded...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.47,1:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}旧书暨杂物一批{\r}\Nwith a donation of used books and sundries.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.24,1:06:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们相信上述款物足以满足阁下所需 此事就此告一段落{\r}\NWe trust this will fill your needs. We now consider the matter closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.57,1:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}恳请阁下勿复来函"{\r}\NPlease stop sending us letters."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.61,1:06:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}典狱长回来之前清理干净{\r}\NClear all this out before the warden gets back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.51,1:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}知道了{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.95,1:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}干得好安迪!{\r}\NGood for you, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哇哦!{\r}\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.42,1:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只用了六年时间{\r}\NIt only took six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.93,1:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在开始 我每星期写两封信{\r}\NFrom now on, I'll write two letters a week instead of one.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.86,1:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你可真够倔的 你最好照他说的把这儿收拾干净{\r}\NI believe you're crazy enough. Get this stuff out...like he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.50,1:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我现在去撇大条{\r}\NI've got to pinch a loaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.10,1:07:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等我出来的时候{\r}\NWhen I come back...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.77,1:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不想再见到这些东西 好吗?{\r}\Nthis is all gone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.38,1:07:28.78,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}费加罗的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.29,1:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪 那是什么声音?{\r}\NDo you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.43,1:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩?{\r}\NDufresne!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.68,1:09:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩?{\r}\N
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.13,1:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪 让我出去!{\r}\NAndy, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.81,1:09:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪?{\r}\NAndy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.67,1:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪?{\r}\NAndy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.54,1:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我至今仍不知晓那两个意大利娘们儿在唱什么{\r}\NI have no idea to this day what those two Italian ladies were singing about.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.78,1:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}话说回来 我也不想知道{\r}\NTruth is, I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.21,1:09:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有些东西是无需言传的{\r}\NSome things are best left unsaid.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.28,1:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我更相信那是因为它的美{\r}\NI like to think it was something so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.22,1:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}超出了语言所能形容的范畴{\r}\Nit can't be expressed in words...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.56,1:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它美得让你为之心碎{\r}\Nand makes your heart ache because of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.13,1:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只能告诉你 那声音直入云霄{\r}\NI tell you, those voices soared...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.90,1:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}比这个灰暗角落里任何人所能梦想到的都更高更远{\r}\Nhigher and farther than anybody in a gray place dares to dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.40,1:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像一只美丽的小鸟 飞进我们乏味的牢笼{\r}\NIt was like a beautiful bird flapped into our drab cage...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.97,1:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}高墙因之消逝于无形之间{\r}\Nand made those walls dissolve away.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.18,1:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就是那一刻{\r}\NAnd for the briefest of moments...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.58,1:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每一个关在肖申克的失足者都触摸到了自由{\r}\Nevery last man at Shawshank felt free.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.15,1:10:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但这却惹得典狱长大发雷霆{\r}\NIt pissed the warden off something awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.12,1:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把门打开!{\r}\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.02,1:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}开门!{\r}\NOpen it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.09,1:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩 给我开门!{\r}\NDufresne, open this door!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.17,1:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把它关掉!{\r}\NTurn that off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.44,1:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我警告你 杜弗瑞恩! 把它关掉!{\r}\NI am warning you. Turn that off!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.41,1:10:47.61,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}小兔乖乖! ; )
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.63,1:10:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}该我收拾你了!{\r}\NYou're mine now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.60,1:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪的惊艳一枪给他带来了两周的禁闭{\r}\NAndy got two weeks in the hole for that little stunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.04,1:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}站起来!{\r}\NOn your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.81,1:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 看看谁来了? - 艺术大师!{\r}\N- Hey, look who's here. - Maestro!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.98,1:11:13.48,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}美国乡村摇滚音乐的标志性人物
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.98,1:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你就不能放点好听的吗 嗯? 比如汉克·威廉姆斯?{\r}\NYou couldn't play something good, huh? Like Hank Williams?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.98,1:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我还没来得及接受点播 他们就冲进来了{\r}\NThey broke the door down before I could take requests.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.99,1:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 两个星期 犯得上吗? - 我经历过最轻松的一段时光!{\r}\N- Was it worth two weeks? - Easiest time I ever did.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.32,1:11:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}扯淡 在这破地方就没轻松时光可言 那小黑屋里呆一周就像一年!{\r}\N- Bullshit! No such thing as easy time in the hole. - A week in the hole is like a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.98,1:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是他妈像一年! 我有莫扎特先生陪我!{\r}\N- Damn straight.  - I had Mr. Mozart to keep me company.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.23,1:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们还能让你背台电唱机进去啊?{\r}\NSo they let you tote that record player down there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.64,1:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它在我脑子里{\r}\NIt was in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.84,1:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在我心里{\r}\NIn here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.21,1:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是音乐的美妙所在 他们...{\r}\NThat's the beauty of music. They...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.51,1:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}无法把它从你这儿夺走{\r}\Ncan't get that from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.38,1:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们对音乐没有这种感受吗?{\r}\NHaven't you ever felt that way about music?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.55,1:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我年轻那会儿曾经吹过口琴{\r}\NWell, I played a mean harmonica as a younger man.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.72,1:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}进来以后也就没兴趣了{\r}\NLost interest in it, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.09,1:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在大牢里没多大意义{\r}\NDidn't make much sense in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.56,1:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这儿才是它最有价值的地方{\r}\NHere's where it makes the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.38,1:12:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有了它你才不会忘记{\r}\NYou need it so you don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.21,1:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}忘记?{\r}\NForget?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.30,1:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}忘记这世上...有一些地方...不是用石头围起来的{\r}\NForget that there are...places...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.54,1:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在你内心深处...有一些东西...{\r}\Nin the world that aren't made out of stone. There's something...inside...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.88,1:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是他们夺不走...摸不到的 只属于你一个人{\r}\Nthat they can't get to...that they can't touch. That's yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.92,1:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你在说什么?{\r}\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.56,1:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望{\r}\NHope.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.86,1:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望?{\r}\NHope.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.13,1:12:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我坦白告诉你 我的朋友{\r}\NLet me tell you something, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.93,1:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望是一种危险品{\r}\NHope is a dangerous thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.40,1:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望使人疯狂{\r}\NHope can drive a man insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.47,1:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它在大牢里没有用{\r}\NIt's got no use on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.81,1:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你得学会接受现实{\r}\NYou'd better get used to that idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.51,1:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}像布鲁克斯那样?{\r}\NLike Brooks did?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.37,1:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}坐吧!{\r}\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.71,1:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你因被判终身监禁己在此服刑三十年了{\r}\NSays here that you've served 30 years of a life sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.18,1:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你认为你已经改过自新了吗?{\r}\NYou feel you've been rehabilitated?
