Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.14,1:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那我们应该把它归到"教育"类 对吧?{\r}\NWe ought to file that under "Educational" too, oughtn't we?
