Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.58,1:17:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到了肯尼迪遇刺那一年{\r}\NBy the year Kennedy was shot...
