Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.63,1:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}提出著名的"出监服刑"计划的一年{\r}\Ninstituted his famous "Inside Out" program.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.04,1:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许你看到过这件事的新闻{\r}\NYou may remember reading about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.34,1:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当时曾充斥各类报纸 他的照片还上过《展望》杂志{\r}\NIt made the papers and got his picture in Look magazine.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.64,1:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这不是放任自流{\r}\NIt's no free ride...
