Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.58,1:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}服刑和改造模式{\r}\Nin corrections and rehabilitation.
