Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.73,1:18:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对纳税人而言 可将开销降至最低{\r}\Nat a bare minimum of expense to Mr. And Mrs. John Q. Taxpayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.41,1:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当然 诺顿不会跟报界说明{\r}\NOf course he didn't tell the press...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.94,1:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"最低开销"其实是个相当不靠谱的噱头{\r}\Nthat "bare minimum of expense" is a fairly loose term.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.61,1:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他有一百种不同的办法暗渡陈仓{\r}\NThere are 100 different ways to skim off the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.85,1:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}人工 材料 你想怎么算就怎么算{\r}\NMen, materials, you name it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.68,1:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦上帝 金钱就这样滚滚而来!{\r}\NAnd oh, my Lord, how the money rolled in!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.79,1:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这样下去 我就没法干了{\r}\NAt this rate, you'll put me out of business.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.52,1:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你守着这些工奴 全城的承包商都没法跟你杀价{\r}\NWith this pool of slave labor, you can underbid any contractor in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.53,1:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们这是在为社会提供有价值的服务{\r}\NWe're providing a valuable community service.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.70,1:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}记者当然爱听你这套话 可我还得养家糊口呢{\r}\NThat's fine for the papers, but I've got a family to feed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.10,1:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}山姆...山姆 我们处的时间也不短了{\r}\NWe go back a long way.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.87,1:19:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我真的需要这份高速公路合同 如果拿不到 说实话我就废了{\r}\NI need this highway contract. I don't get it and I go under. That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.71,1:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你尝尝这些馅饼{\r}\NYou have some of this fine pie...
