Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.34,1:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请一定替我谢谢你太太烤这么好的馅饼{\r}\NYou be sure and thank Maisie for this fine pie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.51,1:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每一笔暗箱操作{\r}\NAnd behind every shady deal...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.01,1:20:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}赚来的每一块钱{\r}\Nbehind every dollar earned...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.91,1:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}都是由安迪经手做账的{\r}\Nthere was Andy, keeping the books.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.38,1:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}两笔存款{\r}\NTwo deposits.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.88,1:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}缅因州国家银行和新英格兰第一银行 照例办夜间存款{\r}\NMaine National and New England First. Night drops as always, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.22,1:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把我东西送到洗衣房 两套衣服要干洗 还有古董架上那个包{\r}\NGet my stuff to the laundry. Two suits for dry-clean and a bag of whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.02,1:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}告诉他们如果再把我的衬衫浆过了头 我就过去教教他们!{\r}\NIf they over-starch my shirts again, they'll hear from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.76,1:20:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我看上去怎么样? - 非常好!{\r}\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.13,1:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}波特兰大道有个大型慈善晚会 州长会去!{\r}\N- Very nice. - Big charity to-do up Portland way. Governor will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.77,1:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}剩下这些给你吧?{\r}\NYou want the rest of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.57,1:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}女人只能烤出恶心的东西{\r}\NWoman can't bake worth shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.74,1:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢你 先生{\r}\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.91,1:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我听说这样的馅饼他收了不少{\r}\NHe's got his fingers in a lot of pies, from what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.35,1:21:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有些手段你做梦都想不到 层层的回扣{\r}\NHe's got scams you haven't even dreamed of. IKickbacks on his kickbacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.39,1:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}黑钱像河一样流过这里{\r}\NA river of dirty money running through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.96,1:21:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他迟早得解释钱是从哪儿来的{\r}\NSooner or later, he'll have to explain where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.99,1:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是他用得着我的地方了{\r}\NThat's where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.36,1:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我让这些钱流通 洗白 汇集{\r}\NI channel it. Filter it. Funnel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.86,1:21:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}股票、证券、国库券...{\r}\NStocks, securities, tax-free municipals.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.03,1:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我把钱撒出去 等它们回来的时候...{\r}\NI send it out into the real world, and when it comes back...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.77,1:21:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 干净得就像个处女穴 嗯? - 比那更干净{\r}\N- Clean as a virgin's honeypot, huh? - Cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.34,1:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到诺顿退休的时候 我已让他成为百万富翁了{\r}\NBy the time Norton retires, I'll have made him a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.28,1:21:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果被抓住的话 他岂不是得在这儿给自己编个号儿啊?{\r}\NIf they ever catch on, he'll wind up in here wearing a number himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.88,1:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我还以为你很信得过我呢{\r}\NI thought you had more faith in me than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.79,1:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你很能干 但那么多文件总会留下蛛丝马迹{\r}\NI know you're good, but all that paper leaves a trail.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.02,1:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果有人想追究 FBI 国税局...{\r}\NNow anybody gets curious, FBI, IRS...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.63,1:22:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}无论如何{\r}\Nwhatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.06,1:22:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总会有人被扯出来{\r}\NIt'll lead to somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.56,1:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那当然 但不会是我 当然也不会是典狱长{\r}\NSure it is, but not to me, and certainly not to the warden.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.81,1:22:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧 是谁呢?{\r}\NAll right, who?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.01,1:22:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}兰度·史蒂文!{\r}\NRandall Stevens.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.14,1:22:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是谁?{\r}\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.28,1:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}沉默寡言的搭档{\r}\NThe "silent" silent partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.48,1:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他是那个有罪的人 帐户的所有者{\r}\NHe's the guilty one, the man with the bank accounts.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.75,1:22:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是洗钱流程的起点{\r}\NIt's where the filtering process starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.12,1:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果有人追查 顶多查到他那儿{\r}\NThey trace anything, it'll just lead to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.59,1:22:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他是什么人?{\r}\NBut who is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.02,1:22:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他是一个幻影 幽灵 是兔子哈维的二表哥{\r}\NHe's a phantom, an apparition. Second cousin to Harvey the Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.09,1:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我凭空...变出来的!{\r}\NI conjured him...out of thin air.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.63,1:22:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他只是个活在文件中的人{\r}\NHe doesn't exist, except on paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.44,1:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是你不可能就这么造个人出来{\r}\NYou can't just make a person up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.01,1:22:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当然可以 只要你知道制度的运作模式{\r}\NSure you can, if you know how the system works.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.61,1:22:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}更令你吃惊的是邮件就能帮你做到{\r}\NIt's amazing what you can accomplish by mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.78,1:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}史蒂文先生有出生证明书{\r}\NMr. Stevens has a birth certificate...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.62,1:22:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}驾驶执照和社保号码{\r}\Ndriver's license, Social Security.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.02,1:22:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你别忽悠我!{\r}\NYou're shitting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.22,1:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们追查帐户 就像是去雕刻一个我想象中的虚幻物{\r}\NIf they trace any accounts, they'll wind up chasing...a figment of my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.73,1:23:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}靠 果然精英人士!{\r}\NWell, I'll be damned!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.06,1:23:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我是不是早就说过你很能干?{\r}\NDid I say you were good?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.16,1:23:12.79,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}荷兰画家 17世纪欧洲最伟大的画家之一
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.16,1:23:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}妈的 你简直是当代伦布兰特{\r}\NShit, you are Rembrandt.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.53,1:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}讽刺的是{\r}\NThe funny thing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.47,1:23:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在外面 我是个正直的人 宁折不弯{\r}\Non the outside, I was an honest man, straight as an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.97,1:23:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}却不得不到监狱里来作一个骗子{\r}\NI had to come to prison to be a crook.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.18,1:23:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你苦恼过吗?{\r}\NEver bother you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.92,1:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}点子不是我出的 我只是处理收益{\r}\NI don't run the scams. I just process the profits.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.26,1:23:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是条很好的分界线 也许是{\r}\NA fine line, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.83,1:23:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好在我还建起了图书馆{\r}\Nbut I also built that library...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.10,1:23:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在那儿帮兄弟们拿到高中文凭{\r}\Nand used it to help guys get their high school diploma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.33,1:23:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}否则你以为他凭什么让我做这些事?{\r}\NWhy do you think he lets me do all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.77,1:23:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让你开心 好帮他运作"洗衣房"...{\r}\NKeep you happy and doing the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.17,1:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}洗的是钱而不是床单而已{\r}\NMoney instead of sheets.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.00,1:23:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的 好让我心甘情愿 算是交换条件{\r}\NWell, I work cheap. That's the tradeoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.86,1:24:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}汤米·威廉姆斯被送进肖申克来是在1965年{\r}\NTommy Williams came to Shawshank in 1965...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.73,1:24:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被判两年徒刑 罪名是"B&E"{\r}\Non a two-year stretch for B & E.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.20,1:24:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就是破门入室闯进你家的意思{\r}\NThat's breaking and entering to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.80,1:24:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}警察在一家JC Penney便利店后门发现他抱台电视机正想开溜{\r}\NCops caught him sneaking TV sets out the back door of a JC Penney.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.47,1:24:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}小混混{\r}\NYoung punk.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.97,1:24:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"摇滚"先生{\r}\NMr. Rock 'n' Roll...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.81,1:24:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}目空一切{\r}\Ncocky as hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.54,1:24:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 老头子们 黏糊得跟糖浆一样{\r}\NCome on, old boys. Moving like molasses!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.18,1:24:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们拖我后腿嘛!{\r}\NMaking me look bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.15,1:24:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们马上就喜欢上他了{\r}\NWe liked him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.18,1:24:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我从门里退出来 就这样抱着电视机{\r}\NI'm backing out the door and I got the TV like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.22,1:24:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那东西太大了 我他妈啥都看不到 然后我听到一个声音{\r}\NA big old thing. I couldn't see shit. Then I hear this voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.49,1:24:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"别动 小子 把手举过头顶!"{\r}\N"Freeze, kid, hands in the air."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.66,1:24:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只好站在那里 抱着电视机 那声音又说{\r}\NI was standing there, holding onto that TV. Finally the voice says:
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.33,1:24:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"你听到我的话了吗? " 我说 "是的先生 我也想举手"{\r}\N"You hear what I said, boy?" I say, " Yes, sir. I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.33,1:24:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"但如果我把这东西丢下 你会加告我毁坏财物的"{\r}\NBut if I drop this, you get me on destruction of property too."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.28,1:25:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}嘿 你在卡士曼蹲过 是吗?{\r}\NYou done some stretch in Cashman, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.08,1:25:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的 那儿要好过得多{\r}\NYeah, that was an easy piece of time, let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.32,1:25:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}周末休假 工作也有条理{\r}\NWeekend furloughs. Work programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.45,1:25:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不像这里 看来你在新英格兰哪儿都蹲过{\r}\NNot like here. Sounds like you done time all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.59,1:25:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我十三岁开始就到处蹲班房了{\r}\NI've been in and out since I was 13.
