Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.33,1:36:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他是这么说的!{\r}\NThat's what the man said.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.68,1:36:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}典狱长?{\r}\NWarden?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.63,1:36:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}汤米!{\r}\N
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.60,1:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}汤米 我要你对这次谈话的内容绝对保密!{\r}\NI'm asking you to keep this conversation just between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.27,1:36:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}此事相当棘手!{\r}\NI feel awkward enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.99,1:36:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这儿有人的判决似乎出了问题{\r}\NWe got a situation here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.92,1:36:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想你也意识到了这一点{\r}\NI think you can appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.23,1:37:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的! 先生 这我能看出来!{\r}\NYes, sir. I sure can.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.40,1:37:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说实话 孩子 这件事让我坐卧不安{\r}\NI tell you, son, this thing really came along and knocked my wind out.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.90,1:37:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}夜不能寐 真的!{\r}\NIt's got me up nights. That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.14,1:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么是该做的正确的事?{\r}\NThe right thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.24,1:37:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}时常难于厘清{\r}\Nsometimes it's hard to know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.98,1:37:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你能理解吗?{\r}\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.72,1:37:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我需要你的帮助 孩子{\r}\NI need your help, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.75,1:37:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果我打算有所行动{\r}\NIf I'm going to move on this...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.26,1:37:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就不能有哪怕一丝一毫的疑点{\r}\Nthere can't be the least little shred of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.16,1:37:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我必须知道{\r}\NI have to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.43,1:37:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你跟杜弗瑞恩所说的事是否属实?{\r}\Nif what you told Dufresne was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.26,1:37:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是的先生 千真万确!{\r}\NYes, sir. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.33,1:37:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么你愿意在法官和陪审团面前...{\r}\NWould you be willing to swear before a judge and jury...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.54,1:37:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}手按圣经...{\r}\Nwith your hand on the Good Book...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.74,1:37:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}向万能的上帝发誓吗?{\r}\Nand take an oath before Almighty God himself?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.61,1:37:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只要你给我这个机会!{\r}\NJust give me that chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.68,1:37:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那也正是我的期许!{\r}\NThat's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.10,1:38:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想你已经听说了...{\r}\NI'm sure by now you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.77,1:38:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}太可惜了{\r}\NTerrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.40,1:38:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么年青的一个人{\r}\NA man that young...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.21,1:38:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还剩不到一年 居然想去越狱{\r}\Nless than a year to go, trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.34,1:38:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哈德利被迫开枪 为此内疚不已{\r}\NBroke Captain Hadley's heart to shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.58,1:39:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}真的伤心透了!{\r}\NTruly, it did.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.08,1:39:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们还是忘记从前的事{\r}\NWe just have to put it behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.19,1:39:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}继续生活{\r}\NMove on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.02,1:39:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我完了!{\r}\NI'm done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.83,1:39:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一切都结束了!{\r}\NEverything stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.43,1:39:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}找其他人帮你做吧!{\r}\NGet someone else to run your scams.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.03,1:39:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有什么会结束!{\r}\NNothing stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.20,1:39:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不会!{\r}\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.77,1:39:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}否则叫你在这儿熬不下去{\r}\NOr you will do the hardest time there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.28,1:39:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}再也不会有看守保护你{\r}\NNo more protection from the guards.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.81,1:39:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我把你从单人牢房扔到鸡奸犯伙儿里{\r}\NI'll pull you out of that 1 -bunk Hilton and cast you down with the sodomites.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.12,1:39:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你会知道被火车操是什么滋味{\r}\NYou'll think you've been fucked by a train.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.96,1:39:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}图书馆?{\r}\NAnd the library?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.13,1:39:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没了!{\r}\NGone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.73,1:39:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}用砖头一块一块封掉!{\r}\NSealed off, brick by brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.76,1:39:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们在操场上把书点了 弄烧烤吃{\r}\NWe'll have us a little book barbecue in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.63,1:39:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}几英里以外都能看得见火光{\r}\NThey'll see the flames for miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.97,1:39:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们像土著人那样围在火边跳舞{\r}\NWe'll dance around it like wild Injuns.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.07,1:40:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你明白我的意思了吗? 听懂了吗?{\r}\NYou understand me? Catching my drift?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.81,1:40:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或许我很愚钝?{\r}\NOr am I being obtuse?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.46,1:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}再给他一个月时间考虑!{\r}\NGive him another month to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.25,1:41:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我妻子曾说我是个很难理解的人{\r}\NMy wife used to say I'm a hard man to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.12,1:41:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}像一本合起来的书{\r}\NLike a closed book.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.35,1:41:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她总这样埋怨我{\r}\NComplained about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.32,1:41:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她很漂亮!{\r}\NShe was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.29,1:41:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}老天 我那么爱她!{\r}\NGod, I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.53,1:41:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可我不知道如何表达 仅此而已!{\r}\NI didn't know how to show it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.50,1:41:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是我害了她 瑞德!{\r}\NI killed her, Red.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.04,1:41:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}虽然不是我开的枪{\r}\NI didn't pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.27,1:41:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是我把她赶上死路的!{\r}\Nbut I drove her away.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.51,1:41:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那就是她的死因 全是因我而起!{\r}\NThat's why she died, because of me...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.41,1:41:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我对她的态度!{\r}\Nthe way I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.20,1:42:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那并不能把你等同于杀人凶手{\r}\NThat don't make you a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.99,1:42:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或许只是个不称职的丈夫{\r}\NBad husband, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.40,1:42:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你可以为此难过 但开枪的不是你!{\r}\NFeel bad about it if you want, but you didn't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.87,1:42:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对 不是我!{\r}\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.61,1:42:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是其他人!{\r}\NSomebody else did.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.78,1:42:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而我却被关在这儿舔伤口!{\r}\NAnd I wound up in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.35,1:42:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}运气太差 我想是{\r}\NBad luck, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.15,1:42:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}霉运四处漂荡{\r}\NIt floats around.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.03,1:42:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总会有人碰上{\r}\NIt's got to land on somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.17,1:42:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}刚巧轮到我 而已{\r}\NIt was my turn, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.36,1:42:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我刚好挡了飓风的道!{\r}\NI was in the path of the tornado.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.07,1:42:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只是没想到这场风暴会刮这么久!{\r}\NI just didn't expect the storm would last as long as it has.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.38,1:42:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}想过你有一天能出去吗?{\r}\NThink you'll ever get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.31,1:42:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我?{\r}\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.32,1:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有啊!{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.65,1:43:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等到我头发花白 丢三拉四 骑驴找驴的那天吧!{\r}\NOne day, when I got a long, white beard...and two or three marbles rolling around upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.36,1:43:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我告诉你我会去哪儿{\r}\NI tell you where I'd go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.47,1:43:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}芝华塔尼欧{\r}\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.00,1:43:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哪里?{\r}\NSay what?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.50,1:43:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}芝华塔尼欧{\r}\NZihuatanejo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.27,1:43:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在墨西哥{\r}\NIt's in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.31,1:43:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}太平洋中的一个小地方{\r}\NA little place on the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.58,1:43:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你知道墨西哥人怎么说太平洋的吗? 不知道!{\r}\NYou know what the Mexicans say about the Pacific?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.18,1:43:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们说那里是没有回忆的地方{\r}\NThey say it has no memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.15,1:43:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那就是我想渡过余生的地方{\r}\NThat's where I want to live the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.46,1:43:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个温暖的没有回忆的地方{\r}\NA warm place with no memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.20,1:43:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}开间小酒店{\r}\NOpen up a little hotel...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.83,1:43:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就在海滩边上{\r}\Nright on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.94,1:43:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}买艘便宜的二手船{\r}\NBuy some worthless old boat...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.67,1:43:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}修葺一新{\r}\Nand fix it up new.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.04,1:43:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}载着我的客人出海{\r}\NTake my guests out...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.11,1:44:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}包船钓鱼{\r}\Ncharter fishing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.32,1:44:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}芝华塔尼欧?{\r}\NZihuatanejo?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.59,1:44:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在那儿 我需要一个能搞到东西的人{\r}\NIn a place like that, I could use a man that knows how to get things.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.00,1:44:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想我适应不了外面的世界 安迪...{\r}\NI don't think I could make it on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.42,1:44:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我大半辈子都关在这儿{\r}\NI been in here most of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.01,1:44:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我已经离不开这里了{\r}\NI'm an institutional man now.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.68,1:44:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像布鲁克斯{\r}\NJust like Brooks was.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.88,1:44:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别低估自己!{\r}\NYou underestimate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.15,1:44:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我觉得没有!{\r}\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.59,1:44:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在这儿我当然能替你搞来东西 但是...{\r}\NIn here I'm the guy who can get things for you, sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.30,1:44:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在外面你只要有本黄页就成了{\r}\Noutside all you need is the Yellow Pages.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.03,1:44:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}见鬼 我不想知道怎么开始的!{\r}\NHell, I wouldn't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.40,1:45:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}太平洋?{\r}\NPacific Ocean?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.44,1:45:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}靠!{\r}\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.04,1:45:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么大的地方会吓死我的!{\r}\NScare me to death, something that big.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.44,1:45:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不会!{\r}\NNot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.95,1:45:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没杀我妻子 我也没杀她的情人{\r}\NI didn't shoot my wife, and I didn't shoot her lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.45,1:45:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不论我犯了什么错 我都已补偿过了{\r}\NWhatever mistakes I made, I've paid for them and then some.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.72,1:45:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一间酒店 一条船{\r}\NThat hotel, that boat...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.99,1:45:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想我要的并不过份!{\r}\NI don't think that's too much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.13,1:45:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我劝你别那么想了{\r}\NYou shouldn't be doing this to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.77,1:45:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那只是你的狗屁白日梦!{\r}\NThis is just shitty pipe dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.24,1:45:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}墨西哥远在天边 而你近在眼前!{\r}\NMexico is way down there and you're in here...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.91,1:45:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是现实!{\r}\Nand that's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.81,1:45:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说的对 这是现实!{\r}\NYeah, right. That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.15,1:45:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它在天边 我在眼前!{\r}\NIt's down there and I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.12,1:45:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}该做个简单的选择了!{\r}\NI guess it comes down to a simple choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.76,1:45:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要么忙着活...{\r}\NGet busy living...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.63,1:45:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要么忙着死!{\r}\Nor get busy dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.34,1:46:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪!{\r}\NAndy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.18,1:46:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德{\r}\NRed.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.77,1:46:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你能出去的话 帮我个忙{\r}\NIf you ever get out of here, do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.71,1:46:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没问题 安迪 任何事都行!{\r}\NSure, Andy. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.85,1:46:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布克斯顿附近有一大片草场 你知道布克斯顿吗?{\r}\NThere's a big hayfield up near Buxton. You know where Buxton is?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.19,1:46:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那儿有许多草场 有一个很特别...{\r}\N- A lot of hayfields up there. - One in particular.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.52,1:46:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它有一段很长的石墙 靠北那头有棵老橡树{\r}\NIt's got a long rock wall with a big oak tree at the north end.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.66,1:46:31.53,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}美国著名诗人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.66,1:46:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}跟罗伯特·弗罗斯特诗里写的差不多{\r}\NIt's like something out of a Robert Frost poem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.46,1:46:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是我向我妻子求婚的地方{\r}\NIt's where I asked my wife to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.37,1:46:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们曾在那儿野餐{\r}\NWe went there for a picnic...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.87,1:46:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在橡树下亲热{\r}\Nand made love under that oak...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.64,1:46:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我向她求婚 她答应了{\r}\Nand I asked and she said yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.88,1:46:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}答应我 瑞德{\r}\NPromise me, Red.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.55,1:46:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你能出去{\r}\NIf you ever get out...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.38,1:46:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}找到那地方{\r}\Nfind that spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.05,1:46:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在石墙根 有块在缅因州见不到的石头...{\r}\NAt the base of that wall, there's a rock that has no earthly business in Maine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.03,1:47:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一块黑色的火山玻璃石{\r}\NPiece of black, volcanic glass.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.73,1:47:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}下面埋着我给你的东西{\r}\NSomething's buried under it I want you to have.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.17,1:47:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}是什么 安迪?{\r}\NWhat, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.84,1:47:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那儿埋的是什么?{\r}\NWhat's buried under there?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.17,1:47:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这得你去挖出来...{\r}\NYou'll have to pry it up...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.24,1:47:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就知道了{\r}\Nto see.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.38,1:47:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我告诉你们 这小子...{\r}\NNo, I'm telling you. The guy is...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.02,1:47:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他说话时表情怪怪的{\r}\NHe's talking funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.85,1:47:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我真的很担心{\r}\NI'm really worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.96,1:47:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那哥儿几个就上心盯着点{\r}\NLet's keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.59,1:47:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}白天没问题 但整晚他都是一个人啊?{\r}\NThat's fine during the day, but at night he's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.30,1:47:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦 我晕死{\r}\NOh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.77,1:47:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}怎么了?{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.10,1:47:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪今天到货场找过我{\r}\NAndy come down to the loading dock today.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.07,1:47:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他问我要了根绳子{\r}\NHe asked me for a length of rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.37,1:47:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}绳子?{\r}\NRope?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.41,1:47:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}六英尺长{\r}\NSix feet long.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.31,1:47:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你给他了?{\r}\NAnd you gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.55,1:47:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当然 我干嘛不给?{\r}\NSure. Why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.55,1:47:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}天啊! 海伍德!{\r}\NJesus! Heywood.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.72,1:47:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我怎么知道他要干嘛?{\r}\NHow was I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.88,1:48:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不记得布鲁克斯了啊?{\r}\NRemember Brooks Hatlen?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.46,1:48:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 安迪不会走那条路的{\r}\NAndy would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.99,1:48:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}绝对不会!{\r}\NNever.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.13,1:48:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不知道{\r}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.30,1:48:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}人的忍耐是有限度的{\r}\NEvery man has his breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.67,1:48:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 我得回家了!{\r}\NLickety-split. Want to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.24,1:48:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就好了 先生!{\r}\NJust about finished, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.12,1:48:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}今晚有三笔要存!{\r}\NThree deposits tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.73,1:48:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把我的衣服送到洗衣房{\r}\NGet my stuff down to the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.84,1:48:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}再把我的鞋擦了{\r}\NAnd shine my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.67,1:48:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要擦得跟镜子一样! 好的 先生{\r}\N- I want them looking like mirrors. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.11,1:49:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你能回来真好 安迪{\r}\NIt's good having you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.51,1:49:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不在的时候真是乱套了{\r}\NPlace wasn't the same without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.26,1:49:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}熄灯!{\r}\NLights out!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.16,1:50:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}记不清我在这里有过多少个难眠之夜{\r}\NI've had some long nights in stir.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.23,1:50:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在黑暗中咀嚼孤独 只有一些心事陪着你{\r}\NAlone in the dark with nothing but your thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.10,1:50:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}时间被拉长得像刀锋那么细{\r}\Ntime can draw out like a blade.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.11,1:50:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而这一夜则是我一生中最漫长的{\r}\NThat was the longest night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.96,1:51:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}清点人数!{\r}\NGive me a count!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.64,1:51:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}南边三楼 到齐!{\r}\NTier 3 south, clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.61,1:51:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}二楼245人犯未到!{\r}\NMan missing on tier 2, cell 245!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.98,1:51:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩!{\r}\NDufresne!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.58,1:51:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快出来! 别跟我耍花样!{\r}\NCome out. You're holding up the show!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.15,1:51:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别等我过去揪你出来 不然我打爆你的头!{\r}\NDon't make me come down or I'll thump your skull for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.13,1:51:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你妈的折腾我 我得赶时间做事!{\r}\NDamn it, you're putting me behind! I got a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.17,1:51:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你最好是病了或者死了 否则我让你去吃屎!{\r}\NYou'd better be sick or dead in there. I shit you not!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.67,1:51:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你听到没有?{\r}\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.11,1:51:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦 我的上帝!{\r}\NOh, my Holy God.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.20,1:52:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}查问这个监区的所有人犯{\r}\NI want every man on this cellblock questioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.20,1:52:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 从他的朋友开始! - 哪个? - 他!{\r}\N- Start with that friend of his. - Who? - Him!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.34,1:52:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}打开237号仓门!{\r}\NOpen 237.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.41,1:52:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你什么意思 "他就是不在这儿了?" 别跟我说这个!{\r}\NWhat do you mean, "He just wasn't here?" Don't say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.95,1:52:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这话我不想听第二遍!{\r}\NDon't tell me that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.48,1:52:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但是长官 他是不在了!{\r}\NBut sir, he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.75,1:52:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我看到了! 海格! 你当我瞎的吗?{\r}\NI can see that, Haig! Think I'm blind?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.89,1:52:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的话是不是这意思?{\r}\NIs that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.49,1:52:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我瞎了吗 海格? - 没有! 长官!{\r}\N- Am I blind, Haig? - No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.06,1:52:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么你呢? 你瞎的吗?{\r}\NWhat about you. You blind?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.06,1:52:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 告诉我这是什么? - 昨晚的查房记录!{\r}\N- Tell me what this is. - Last night's count.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.83,1:52:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}杜弗瑞恩的名字在吗? 我确定在 这儿!{\r}\NYou see Dufresne's name there? I sure do. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.34,1:52:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"杜弗瑞恩！"{\r}\N"Dufresne."
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.34,1:52:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}熄灯的时候他还在牢房里{\r}\NHe was in his cell...at lights out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.21,1:52:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}按道理今早他也应该在牢房里{\r}\NReasonable he'd be here in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.51,1:52:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}马上把他找出来!{\r}\NI want him found.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.35,1:52:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是明天 不是早饭后 就现在!{\r}\NNot tomorrow, not after breakfast. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.05,1:53:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}遵命 长官!{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.25,1:53:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}跟我来 动作快点!{\r}\NLet's go. Move your butts.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.93,1:53:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}站好!{\r}\NStand.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.36,1:53:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说吧?{\r}\NWell?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.87,1:53:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说什么?{\r}\NWell, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.07,1:53:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你们俩整天粘在一起 狼狈为奸{\r}\NI see you two all the time. You're thick as thieves, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.61,1:53:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他肯定对你说过什么{\r}\NHe must have said something.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.84,1:53:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有 长官!{\r}\NNo, sir, Warden.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.74,1:53:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个字都没有!{\r}\NNot a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.55,1:53:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}主啊 这是个神迹!{\r}\NLord, it's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.72,1:53:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个大活人像风中放的屁一样没了{\r}\NMan vanished like a fart in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.95,1:53:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}整个消失了{\r}\NNothing left...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.95,1:53:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就剩下窗台上几块破石头{\r}\Nbut some damn rocks on a windowsill.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.89,1:53:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有个墙上的小妞 问问她吧{\r}\NAnd that cupcake on the wall. Let's ask her.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.83,1:53:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许她知道{\r}\NMaybe she knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.83,1:53:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你说什么水裤妞儿? 想谈谈吗?{\r}\NWhat say there, fuzzy-britches? Feel like talking?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.91,1:53:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}喔 当然不会!{\r}\NGuess not.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.87,1:53:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她凭什么知道的多一些?{\r}\NWhy should she be any different?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.14,1:53:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是一个阴谋!{\r}\NThis is a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.44,1:53:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没别的解释!{\r}\NThat's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.88,1:54:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个他妈的大阴谋!{\r}\NOne big, damn conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.88,1:54:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所有人都有份儿!{\r}\NAnd everyone's in on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.52,1:54:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}包括她!{\r}\NIncluding her!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.72,1:54:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}1966年{\r}\NIn 1966...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.62,1:54:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪·杜弗瑞恩从肖申克监狱逃脱{\r}\NAndy Dufresne escaped...from Shawshank Prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.03,1:54:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们追查到的只有一套泥泞的囚衣...{\r}\NAll they found was a muddy set of prison clothes...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.23,1:54:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一块肥皂...{\r}\Na bar of soap...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.97,1:54:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}还有一把很旧的鹤嘴槌{\r}\Nand an old rock hammer...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.73,1:54:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}槌头几乎要被磨光了{\r}\Ndamn near worn down to the nub.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.71,1:55:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我曾认为用它挖六百年才能挖穿围墙的隧道{\r}\NI had thought it'd take a man 600 years to tunnel through the wall with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.11,1:55:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪只用了不到二十年就办到了{\r}\NOld Andy did it in less than 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.03,1:55:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪热爱地质学{\r}\NOh, Andy loved geology.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.10,1:55:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我肯定这源自于他一丝不苟的性格{\r}\NI imagine it appealed to his meticulous nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.67,1:55:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}正如曾经的冰河时期造就了千百万年的山脉一般{\r}\NAn ice age here...million years of mountain building there.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.45,1:55:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}地质学是关于压力和时间的研究{\r}\NGeology is the study of pressure and time.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.52,1:55:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而这也正是他面临的全部问题{\r}\NThat's all it takes, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.85,1:55:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}压力...{\r}\NPressure...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.59,1:55:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}和时间...{\r}\Nand time.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.19,1:55:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当然还有一张大海报{\r}\NThat and a big goddamn poster.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.30,1:55:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像我所说的{\r}\NLike I said...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.73,1:56:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在监狱里 每个人都会找些事情把脑子塞满{\r}\Nin prison, a man will do anything to keep his mind occupied.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.54,1:56:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看来安迪最喜欢的是把他的墙壁搬运到操场上{\r}\NSeems Andy's favorite hobby was toting his wall out into the exercise yard...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.88,1:56:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一次满满两把{\r}\Na handful at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.11,1:56:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我估计汤米被杀后{\r}\NI guess after Tommy was killed...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.38,1:56:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪认定他在这儿已经呆够了{\r}\NAndy decided he'd been here long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.55,1:56:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}快点 我得回家了!{\r}\NLickety-split. I want to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.85,1:56:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就好了 先生!{\r}\NI'm just about finished, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.34,1:56:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}今晚有三笔要存!{\r}\NThree deposits tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.59,1:56:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪按照吩咐{\r}\NAndy did like he was told.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.09,1:57:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把鞋擦得闪闪发亮{\r}\NBuffed those shoes to a high mirror-shine.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.26,1:57:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}守卫完全没有注意到{\r}\NThe guards simply didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.87,1:57:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也没有{\r}\NNeither did I.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.53,1:57:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说认真的{\r}\NI mean, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.27,1:57:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谁会没事干去盯别人穿什么鞋子呢?{\r}\Nhow often do you really look at a man's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.83,1:59:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪爬向自由 穿过恶臭满盈的五百码{\r}\NAndy crawled to freedom through 500 yards...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.23,1:59:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我简直想都不敢想那有多臭{\r}\Nof shit-smelling foulness I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.57,1:59:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或许我只是不愿去想{\r}\NOr maybe I just don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.31,1:59:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}五百码{\r}\NFive hundred yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.18,1:59:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有五个橄榄球场那么长{\r}\NThat's the length of five football fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.88,1:59:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}差不多有半英里{\r}\NJust shy of half a mile.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.68,2:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}第二天早上 就在拉蔻儿的小秘密被揭穿的同时{\r}\NThe next morning, right about the time Raquel was spilling her secret...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.58,2:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一位与任何人都素昧平生的男子{\r}\Na man nobody ever laid eyes on before...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.65,2:00:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}来到缅因州国家银行{\r}\Nstrolled into the Maine National Bank.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.82,2:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}在此之前 他一直活在文件中{\r}\NUntil that moment, he didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.56,2:00:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我可以帮您吗?{\r}\N- Except on paper. - May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.33,2:00:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他持有所有正确的身份证明文件...{\r}\NHe had all the proper ID...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.46,2:01:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}驾驶执照、出生证明、社保卡...{\r}\Ndriver's license, birth certificate, Social Security card...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.60,2:01:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}签名也完全吻合{\r}\NAnd the signature was a spot-on match.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.34,2:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}非常遗憾失去您这样一位好客户{\r}\NI must say I'm sorry to be losing your business.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.64,2:01:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望你在国外生活愉快!{\r}\NI hope you'll enjoy living abroad.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.17,2:01:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢!{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.94,2:01:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想我会的!{\r}\NI'm sure I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.01,2:01:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}先生 这是你的本票 还有什么能帮您的吗?{\r}\NHere's your cashier's check, sir. Will there be anything else?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.55,2:01:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请问{\r}\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.12,2:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad1\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}能帮我把它寄出去吗?{\r}\NWould you add this to your outgoing mail?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.12,2:01:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}很高兴为您服务!{\r}\NI'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.12,2:01:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 再见! - 走好 先生!{\r}\NGood day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.39,2:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}史蒂文先生那天早上走访了波特兰地区近十二家银行{\r}\NMr. Stevens visited nearly a dozen banks in the Portland area that morning.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.30,2:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}全部算起来{\r}\NAll told, he blew town...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.10,2:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他让典狱长诺顿的三十七万多美元灰飞烟灭{\r}\Nwith better than $370,000 of Warden Norton's money.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.64,2:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}十九年刑期的遣散费{\r}\NSeverance pay for 19 years.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.65,2:01:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}早上好 波特兰号角报!{\r}\NGood morning, Portland Daily Bugle.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.03,2:01:56.46,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肖申克的贪污与谋杀 检察官掌握黑钱证据 检控指日可待
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.87,2:02:04.74,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}主的审判将会迅速降临
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.06,2:02:19.19,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}《圣经》
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.86,2:02:26.19,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}亲爱的典狱长 你说的没错 得救之道 就在其中
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.53,2:02:30.02,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}出埃及记
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.91,2:02:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}拜伦·哈德利? 你有权保持沉默{\r}\NByron Hadley? You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.11,2:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}否则你所说的一切都将成为呈堂证供{\r}\NIf you give up this right, anything you say can be held against you in court.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.78,2:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没有亲眼看到 但我听说拜伦·哈德利{\r}\NI wasn't there to see, but I hear Byron Hadley sobbed like a girl...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.36,2:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}被带走时哭得像个小女生{\r}\Nwhen they took him away.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.13,2:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺顿不愿简单俯首就擒{\r}\NNorton had no intention of going that quietly.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.07,2:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}山姆·诺顿?{\r}\NSamuel Norton.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.71,2:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们有你的拘捕令 开门!{\r}\NWe have a warrant for your arrest. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.88,2:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}把门打开!{\r}\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.52,2:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不知道是哪把钥匙{\r}\NI'm not sure which key.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.93,2:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请你配合 诺顿!{\r}\NMake it easy on yourself, Norton!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.38,2:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我相信最后时刻经过他大脑的{\r}\NI like to think the last thing that went through his head...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.05,2:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}除了一颗子弹{\r}\Nother than that bullet...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.85,2:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一定还有对栽在安迪手里的难以置信和迷惑不解{\r}\Nwas to wonder how the hell Andy Dufresne ever got the best of him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.79,2:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}诺顿一伙倒台不久{\r}\NNot long after the warden deprived us of his company...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.53,2:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我收到一张明信片{\r}\NI got a postcard in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.06,2:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么都没写 邮戳是...{\r}\NIt was blank, but the postmark said...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.10,2:04:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}汉考克口岸 德克萨斯{\r}\NFort Hancock, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.77,2:04:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}汉考克口岸{\r}\NFort Hancock...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.40,2:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就在边境线上{\r}\Nright on the border.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.54,2:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是安迪出境的地方{\r}\NThat's where Andy crossed.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.32,2:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}每当我脑海中浮现他驾着敞篷车一路向南的画面时{\r}\NWhen I picture him heading south in his own car with the top down...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.58,2:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我总会忍不住笑出来{\r}\Nit always makes me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.65,2:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪·杜弗瑞恩{\r}\NAndy Dufresne...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.59,2:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}爬过了臭水沟{\r}\Nwho crawled through a river of shit...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.82,2:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}洗清了罪孽 在彼岸重生{\r}\Nand came out clean on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.06,2:04:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪·杜弗瑞恩{\r}\NAndy Dufresne...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.23,2:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}直奔太平洋而去{\r}\Nheaded for the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.80,2:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哈德利撕住他的领口 对吗?{\r}\NHadley's got him by the throat, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.17,2:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他说 "这鸟人想给自己来一出意外"{\r}\NHe says, " I believe this boy's about to have himself an accident."
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.17,2:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们几个跟他最熟的时常聊起他{\r}\NThose of us who knew him best talk about him often.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.71,2:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我发誓 他有种神奇的魅力{\r}\NI swear, the stuff he pulled...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.61,2:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"我的朋友能有几瓶啤酒"{\r}\N"My friends could use a couple of beers."
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.91,2:05:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他办到了!{\r}\NAnd he got it!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.82,2:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有时我会伤感 因为安迪已经不在了{\r}\NSometimes it makes me sad, though...Andy being gone.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.62,2:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只能提醒自己有些鸟是不能关在笼子里的{\r}\NI have to remind myself that some birds aren't meant to be caged.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.22,2:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它们的羽翼是如此绚丽 光芒夺目{\r}\NTheir feathers are just too bright.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.00,2:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}当它们飞出牢笼时{\r}\NAnd when they fly away...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.47,2:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}会让那些觉得把它们关起来是种罪恶的人感到由衷的喜悦{\r}\Nthe part of you that knows it was a sin to lock them up does rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.64,2:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但同时 它们的离开让你生活的地方空荡荡的{\r}\NBut still...the place you live in is that much more drab and empty that they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.91,2:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可能我只是过于想念我的朋友了{\r}\NI guess I just miss my friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.97,2:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请坐!{\r}\NPlease sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.75,2:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}艾力斯·博伊德·瑞丁（瑞德的全名）{\r}\NEllis Boyd Redding...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.85,2:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你因终身监禁已被关了40年了{\r}\Nyour files say you've served 40 years of a life sentence.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.92,2:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你觉得你改过自新了吗?{\r}\NYou feel you've been rehabilitated?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.92,2:06:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}改过自新?{\r}\NRehabilitated?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.53,2:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}哦 让我想想看{\r}\NWell, now, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.43,2:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我不明白那是什么意思{\r}\NI don't have any idea what that means.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.87,2:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}意思是你已经准备好重返社会...{\r}\NIt means you're ready to rejoin society...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.70,2:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你是怎么想的 老弟{\r}\NI know what you think it means, sonny.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.21,2:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对我来说那只是一个构词法的产物{\r}\NTo me it's just a made-up word.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.55,2:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}给政客们用的词汇{\r}\NA politician's word so that...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.31,2:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让你这样的年轻人能穿西装打领带{\r}\Nyoung fellas like yourself can wear a suit and a tie...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.32,2:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}有事可做{\r}\Nand have a job.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.89,2:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你倒底想知道些什么?{\r}\NWhat do you really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.76,2:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我对自己的罪行感到后悔吗?{\r}\NAm I sorry for what I did?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.57,2:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那么 你后悔吗?{\r}\NWell, are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.64,2:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没有一天我不感到后悔的{\r}\NThere's not a day goes by I don't feel regret.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.84,2:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不是因为我被关在这儿 或者为了迎合你的想法{\r}\NNot because I'm in here or because you think I should.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.78,2:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我回首往事{\r}\NI look back on the way I was then...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.49,2:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个年轻的...愚蠢的孩子铸成大错{\r}\Na young...stupid kid who committed that terrible crime.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.26,2:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想和他谈谈{\r}\NI want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.90,2:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}想和他讲讲人生大义{\r}\NI want to try and talk some sense to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.10,2:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}教教他为人处世之道{\r}\NTell him the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.14,2:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但我做不到{\r}\NBut I can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.78,2:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那孩子早都不在了{\r}\NThat kid's long gone...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.98,2:07:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只剩下你面前这个老头子{\r}\Nand this old man is all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.15,2:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我得跟他继续生活{\r}\NI got to live with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.99,2:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}改过自新?{\r}\NRehabilitated?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.06,2:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只是个狗屁字眼{\r}\NIt's just a bullshit word.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.83,2:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}请你继续 在表格上盖章吧 老弟 别浪费我的时间了{\r}\NSo you go on and stamp your forms, sonny, and stop wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.42,2:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说句实话{\r}\NBecause to tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.03,2:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我根本不在乎!{\r}\NI don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.33,2:08:25.83,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}批准
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.96,2:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的 小姐{\r}\NHere you go, miss.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.30,2:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}可以去趟洗手间吗?{\r}\NRestroom break?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.14,2:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不用每次要小便都来问我 只管去就是了!{\r}\NYou don't need to ask me every time you need to go take a piss. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.72,2:10:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}四十年来我连小便都需要被批准{\r}\NForty years I've been asking permission to piss.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.62,2:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不申请的话一滴都挤不出来{\r}\NI can't squeeze a drop without say-so.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.13,2:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现实是很难面对的{\r}\NThere's a harsh truth to face.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.97,2:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我没办法习惯外面的生活{\r}\NNo way I'm going to make it on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.74,2:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我总在想怎样才能违反假释条例{\r}\NAll I do anymore is think of ways to break my parole...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.25,2:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那样他们会把我送回去{\r}\Nso maybe they'd send me back.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.92,2:10:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}生活在恐惧中是很可怕的事{\r}\NTerrible thing, to live in fear.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.26,2:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}布鲁克斯知道{\r}\NBrooks Hatlen knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.13,2:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他知道得太清楚了{\r}\NKnew it all too well.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.66,2:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我只想回到适合我的地方{\r}\NAll I want is to be back where things make sense.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.50,2:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不用惶惶不可终日的地方{\r}\NWhere I won't have to be afraid all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.24,2:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}只是有一件事阻止了我{\r}\NOnly one thing stops me.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.04,2:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我答应安迪的事{\r}\NA promise I made to Andy.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.97,2:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}到了!{\r}\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.71,2:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}非常感谢 先生!{\r}\NMuch obliged, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:20.70,2:15:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}亲爱的瑞德{\r}\NDear Red:
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.20,2:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}若你能看到这封信 那你已经出来了{\r}\NIf you're reading this, you've gotten out...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.87,2:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}既然你已经跑了这么远 不妨再跑远一点{\r}\Nand if you've come this far, maybe you'd come a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.21,2:15:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你还记得那个地方的名字 是吗?{\r}\NYou remember the name of the town, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.98,2:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}芝华塔尼欧!{\r}\NZihuatanejo!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.12,2:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我需要一个能干的人和我一起完成我的计划{\r}\NI could use a good man to help me get my project on wheels.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.22,2:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我期待你的到来 棋盘已经准备好了{\r}\NI'll keep an eye out for you, and the chessboard ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.56,2:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}记住 瑞德{\r}\NRemember, Red...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.29,2:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}希望是个好东西{\r}\Nhope is a good thing...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.60,2:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许是世间最好的东西{\r}\Nmaybe the best of things.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.80,2:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好东西从不会逝去{\r}\NAnd no good thing ever dies.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.50,2:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望这封信能等到你{\r}\NI will be hoping that this letter finds you...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:57.57,2:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}并能看到你安然无恙{\r}\Nand finds you well.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.81,2:16:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的朋友{\r}\NYour friend...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.24,2:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}安迪{\r}\NAndy.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.24,2:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}"要么忙着活{\r}\N"Get busy living...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.18,2:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要么忙着死"{\r}\Nor get busy dying. "
Dialogue: 0,2:16:42.78,2:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这话太他妈的对了{\r}\NThat's goddamn right.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.62,2:16:49.42,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}瑞德也住过
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.19,2:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是有生以来第二次...{\r}\NFor the second time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.56,2:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我有做贼心虚的感觉{\r}\NI'm guilty of committing a crime.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.20,2:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我担心他们会设下路障 当然 这是因为有人违反假释条例{\r}\NParole violation. Of course I doubt they'll toss up any roadblocks for that.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.13,2:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}而不是为了我这种老家伙{\r}\NNot for an old crook like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.37,2:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}德克萨斯州 汉考克口岸 谢谢!{\r}\NFort Hancock, Texas, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:11.08,2:17:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我发现我很兴奋 如坐针毡 思绪纷乱{\r}\NI find I'm so excited I can barely sit still or hold a thought in my head.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.25,2:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我想这是一个自由人才能感受到的兴奋{\r}\NI think it's the excitement only a free man can feel.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.79,2:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个自由人开始了漫长的旅程{\r}\NA free man at the start of a long journey...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.49,2:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}伴随着未知的结局{\r}\Nwhose conclusion is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.09,2:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望我能越过边界 完成这段旅程{\r}\NI hope I can make it across the border.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:32.26,2:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望见到我的朋友 紧握他的手{\r}\NI hope to see my friend and shake his hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:37.17,2:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望太平洋的海水和我梦中一样蓝{\r}\NI hope the Pacific is as blue as it has been in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.16,2:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我希望...{\r}\NI hope.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.81,2:18:24.71,Default -TOP,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}导演的经纪人和朋友 本片完成前因艾滋病去世
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.81,2:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\fs21\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谨此此片纪念 亚伦·格林
